        // Cowfusion
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Ranol: Yep, that's all of 'em. All my cows accounted for, not one missing. Huh? Watchu looking at, city dweller?",
                "cowfusion-ranol-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Ranol: If I needed any help I'd ask for some. Not my first day workin' a barn. Now shoo!",
                "cowfusion-ranol-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Ranol: A human, eh? All the way out 'ere at the end of the canyon? Yer a tough one.",
                "cowfusion-ranol-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Ranol: Perhaps I can give yer some work, if yer are lookin' for it? Someone's been coming and nabbing my cows!",
                "cowfusion-ranol-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Ranol: 'an I know exactly who it is - that blasted cow scientist that lives in the lab just north of 'ere.",
                "cowfusion-ranol-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Ranol: Anyway, yer up for the job? Can't let 'im just keep stealing them forever!",
                "cowfusion-ranol-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Ranol: His cavern laboratory is just north from 'ere. Not too hard to find. Once yer there, get him to return my cows!",
                "cowfusion-ranol-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Ranol: There's one problem though. The door to the place is always shut, so you'll 'ave to find another way in.",
                "cowfusion-ranol-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ranol: Have yer gone to check out the big laboratory to the North yet? I need my cows back!",
                "cowfusion-ranol-9",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Ranol: What's this 'ere? Ibele, that you? My girl, I knew you'd come back to me!",
                "cowfusion-ranol-10",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Ranol: And to think I was going to hire some city-dwellin' 'uman to get you for me? Ha!",
                "cowfusion-ranol-11",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/3] Ranol: Right then, back into the pen you go. Hup!", "cowfusion-ranol-12", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ranol: What are you doin' out here, ya fool? Back in you go!", "cowfusion-ranol-13", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Ranol: Well well well. So, any excuses for why I haven't heard of yer since I sent yer off to find my cows?",
                "cowfusion-ranol-14",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Ranol: Yer were turned into a cow? That's the best yer can come up with?",
                "cowfusion-ranol-15",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Ranol: I knew yer weren't up to the job, city dweller. If yer didn't want to help yer coulda just said so!",
                "cowfusion-ranol-16",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Suspicious Cow: Moo.", "cowfusion-suspicouscow-1", false);
        s.addSound("[3/3] Suspicious Cow: Password?", "cowfusion-suspicouscow-2", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/8] Suspicious Cow: You're right, there is no password. Just seeing if you can understand me.",
                "cowfusion-suspicouscow-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/8] Suspicious Cow: You're one of us then, the oppressed? Want to break free from these farmers? Well aren't you in luck.",
                "cowfusion-suspicouscow-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/8] Suspicious Cow: I can help you with that. WE can help you with that.",
                "cowfusion-suspicouscow-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/8] Suspicious Cow: Our people have a secret hideout not far from here. It's located right under that barn just behind me.",
                "cowfusion-suspicouscow-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/8] Suspicious Cow: It may seem close, but unless you've been practicing your athletics, you won't be able to get over these fences.",
                "cowfusion-suspicouscow-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/8] Suspicious Cow: See that haybale in the middle of our pen? I bet you could push and pull it into such a position that'd allow you to climb over the fence with your cow physique.",
                "cowfusion-suspicouscow-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/8] Suspicious Cow: The second pen might have a similar problem, but I'm sure you can figure that our yourself.",
                "cowfusion-suspicouscow-9",
                false);
        s.addSound("[8/8] Suspicious Cow: Good luck!", "cowfusion-suspicouscow-10", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/8] Suspicious Cow: What? What does that even mean? There isn't actually a password! Or did no one tell me that there was? Ah, nevermind, at least you can understand me.",
                "cowfusion-suspicouscow-11",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/2] Suspicious Cow: Moo.", "cowfusion-suspicouscow-12", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Suspicious Cow: If you want to escape, you'll have to push and pull the haybale around so that you can climb over the fences.",
                "cowfusion-suspicouscow-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Receptionist: Oh, a new recruit? We weren't expecting anyone at this time. How'd you find your way in?",
                "cowfusion-receptionist-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Receptionist: Wait, you're different. Something's off about you. Like you've never been in a cow's body before.",
                "cowfusion-receptionist-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Receptionist: Oh. Oh, this is not good. Uhm, you should talk to the boss. He'll probably know what to do with you.",
                "cowfusion-receptionist-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Receptionist: You'll find him in the big office at the very end of this facility. Just stick to the path and don't be nosy, okay?",
                "cowfusion-receptionist-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Receptionist: You need to speak to the boss, he's in his office at the end of the facility.",
                "cowfusion-receptionist-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Receptionist: Oh, hello! You must be the one cow from earlier, right?",
                "cowfusion-receptionist-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Receptionist: Well, Drale says you're welcome to visit whenever you'd like, so... Welcome!",
                "cowfusion-receptionist-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Receptionist: We have many amenities available in this facility, so feel free to make yourself comfortable!",
                "cowfusion-receptionist-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/7] Worker: So you're telling me we've got to move this thing all the way to the factory?",
                "cowfusion-worker1-1",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/7] Worker: Yep.", "cowfusion-worker2-1", false);
        s.addSound("[3/7] Worker: Just the two of us?", "cowfusion-worker1-2", false);
        s.addSound("[4/7] Worker: Yep.", "cowfusion-worker2-2", false);
        s.addSound("[5/7] Worker: With our bare hands? Couldn't even give us a wagon?", "cowfusion-worker1-3", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/7] Worker: Hey, it's for the cause. Remember what you're working towards.",
                "cowfusion-worker2-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/7] Worker: Yeah, yeah, I know. But what's it gonna matter if my back's worse than my grandpa's at the end of this?",
                "cowfusion-worker1-4",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/9] Worker: So. We still haven't moved this thing at all, huh?", "cowfusion-worker1-5", false);
        s.addSound("[2/9] Worker: Nope.", "cowfusion-worker2-4", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/9] Worker: Guess that makes sense. Everyone's been busy talking about... you know.",
                "cowfusion-worker1-6",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/9] Worker: Yep.", "cowfusion-worker2-5", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/9] Worker: Oh, hey, there they are! Hey, you! You're the one that helped Drale free a bunch of our friends from the ranch, right?",
                "cowfusion-worker1-7",
                false);
        s.addSound("[6/9] Worker: Looks like them.", "cowfusion-worker2-6", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/9] Worker: Hey, we never got to thank you for what you did! A lot of us wouldn't be here today if you hadn't. Kyle here definitely wouldn't, heh.",
                "cowfusion-worker1-8",
                false);
        s.addSound("[8/9] Worker: Thanks.", "cowfusion-worker2-7", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[9/9] Worker: Well, I hope we get to see you around some more! We've got to get back to... uh, moving this thing. But, hey, maybe after we can hang out?",
                "cowfusion-worker1-9",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Worker: I'm here for a crate of this wheat stuff. How has the recent batch turned out?",
                "cowfusion-worker3-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Botanist: Same as usual. Growing this stuff underground isn't easy. You can grab a crate on the far left side.",
                "cowfusion-botanist-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Worker: Right, thank you! Y'know, they say this stuff back home is a lot high quality than the stuff the farmers fed us.",
                "cowfusion-worker3-2",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/4] Botanist: Well it won't be too long until we find out.", "cowfusion-botanist-2", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/7] Worker: Hey... Don't, uh, tell anyone I asked... But you wouldn't happen to- happen to have some... barley?",
                "cowfusion-worker3-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/7] Botanist: Woah, there. Calm yourself, friend. You know the rules about that kind of stuff.",
                "cowfusion-botanist-3",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/7] Botanist: ...", "cowfusion-botanist-4", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/7] Botanist: Yeah, okay, here. Here's a package of... stuff. Don't tell anyone you got it from me.",
                "cowfusion-botanist-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/7] Worker: Y-yep, of course! Thank you kindly. I'll make sure... nobody kn-",
                "cowfusion-worker3-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/7] Worker: Oh no. H-hello there, Drale's friend! It's- good to. See you! You didn't happen to, uh-",
                "cowfusion-worker3-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/7] Botanist: Best get moving quick before the word spreads, friend.",
                "cowfusion-botanist-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Worker: Looking for the boss, huh? Well, he's just up ahead in his office, behind the big door. Pretty hard to miss.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Worker: Hey, hope you don't mind me asking, but, uh... Why are you still walking around looking like that?",
                "cowfusion-worker4-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Worker: Eh, I don't judge. You go right ahead, I've got some work to attend to.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Worker: Looking for the boss again, huh? Well, just as always, he's up ahead in his office. Hard to miss, as usual.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Worker: ...So the cow thing wasn't your choice, huh? Could've fooled me. Almost did, really.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Worker: ...Well, this is awkward. Uh. You don't need to talk to me, y'know. Just go on ahead.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-6",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/17] Worker: ... where did you come from?!", "cowfusion-worker4-7", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/17] Worker: You fell into the incinerator? And defeated a mutant cow monster?",
                "cowfusion-worker4-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/17] Worker: Yeah that checks out. So what happened to get you thrown down here?",
                "cowfusion-worker4-9",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/17] Worker: Oh, angered him by pretending to be a cow after already speaking? Yeah, I feel ya. When the boss is in a mood, anything you say could get you thrown down here.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-10",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/17] Worker: Here, why don't you follow me? I'll take you back to him, you can straighten things out, and you'll be back as a human in no time!",
                "cowfusion-worker4-11",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/17] Worker: So... yeah. Drale isn't the best at... conflict resolution. Catch him on a bad day, and he might just throw you in the Pit.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-12",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/17] Worker: I got stationed down here for a week because I interrupted him during his daily yoga session.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/17] Worker: Gerald, over there? He used to be in accounting. Until he forgot to carry the two one day, and... Well, here he is now.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-14",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[9/17] Worker: Drale's alright on a good day, but we've been running out of good days lately! He keeps pulling late hours on this... wholly unnecessary project!",
                "cowfusion-worker4-15",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/17] Worker: He insists we have to keep trying to find our original ship, instead of just building a new one with all the materials we have! It's ridiculous!",
                "cowfusion-worker4-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[11/17] Worker: What ship? Oh, of course, you're not a Woc. See, our race isn't actually from- you know, maybe that's a story for another time.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-17",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[12/17] Worker: For now let's get you back up to the main lab and hopefully Drale will be in a bit of a better mood!",
                "cowfusion-worker4-18",
                false);
        s.addSound("[13/17] Worker: Well, we're here!", "cowfusion-worker4-19", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[14/17] Worker: You head on up that pipe and with a bit of luck it'll plonk you out right in front of Drale.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-20",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[15/17] Worker: If you try explaining the situation again I'm sure he'll be understanding.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-21",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[16/17] Worker: He usually is after he's had some time to cool off.", "cowfusion-worker4-22", false);
        s.addSound("[17/17] Worker: Go on, off you go! It was lovely to meet you.", "cowfusion-worker4-23", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/17] Worker: Pretended to be a cow when you're actually a human? Must have caught him on a rough day to get thrown down for that. Usually he'd just let a cow go.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-24",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/17] Worker: Well, here, why don't you follow me? I'll take you back to him, you can straighten things out, and I'm sure you'll be back as a human in no time!",
                "cowfusion-worker4-25",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/17] Worker: So... yeah. That's Drale. Catch him on a bad day, and he might just throw you in the Pit.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-26",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[12/17] Worker: For now let's get you back up to the main lab and hopefully Drale will be in a bit of a better mood! Maybe mention the human thing this time, alright?",
                "cowfusion-worker4-27",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/17] Worker: ...Oh! You're the one Drale told us to look out for. Accidentally dropped into the Pit, huh?",
                "cowfusion-worker4-28",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/17] Worker: The boss said to apologize to ya for the inconvenience. We've all been workin' late hours recently... Some of us more than others.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-29",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/17] Worker: Anyhow, follow me. I'll take you back to him, and you can talk this out! You'll be back as a human in no time.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-30",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/17] Worker: So... yeah. That's Drale for you. Absentminded as ever. He said something about labeling his levers from now on, so I reckon that's a positive.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-31",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/17] Worker: ...You're a friend of the boss, right? Would you be able to put in a good word for us? Gerald and I have been down here for a while, and we'd like to get back to our normal positions.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-32",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/17] Worker: Drale's alright on a good day, but we've been running out of good days lately! He keeps pulling late hours on this... wholly unnecessary project!",
                "cowfusion-worker4-33",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[9/17] Worker: He insists we have to keep trying to find our original ship, instead of just building a new one with all the materials we have! It's ridiculous!",
                "cowfusion-worker4-34",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/17] Worker: Maybe you'll be able to get through to him, being his friend and all. We've all been stressed, and it's really just...",
                "cowfusion-worker4-35",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[11/17] Worker: Huh? What ship? Oh, right. You're not a Woc. So, you see, our race isn't actually from- you know, maybe that's a story for another time.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-36",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[12/17] Worker: For now let's get you back up to the main lab. Drale will be glad to see you in one piece! He sounded worried for your safety.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-37",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[15/17] Worker: Remember what I told you! Try to put in a good word for us, yeah?",
                "cowfusion-worker4-38",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[16/17] Worker: If not, well... At least I tried. Let the record show I tried.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-39",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[17/17] Worker: ...Alright! Go on, off you go! It was lovely to meet you.",
                "cowfusion-worker4-40",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Worker: What're you waiting for? Get on through that pipe and talk to Drale!",
                "cowfusion-worker4-41",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Drale: Whoop, alright! Don't want you going anywhere, buddy! Uh... What are you doing here, exactly...?",
                "cowfusion-drale-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Drale: You- what? Oh, gosh, how is that even possible? I don't think I had anything that could...",
                "cowfusion-drale-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Drale: Oh! You must've been snooping through my laboratory. That's... okay, we can talk about that later. Did you step into my machine?",
                "cowfusion-drale-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Drale: It's not even meant to turn humans into cows! I just made it to turn the exiles back into Wocs! So how does a human become a cow...?",
                "cowfusion-drale-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Drale: Right, right, sorry. Here, uh- I'll try and get this cage down. Darn controls... Why did I design these so poorly?",
                "cowfusion-drale-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Drale: ...So while I try to figure out which lever to push, tell me about yourself! Anything interesting going on in your life?",
                "cowfusion-drale-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Drale: You... You are? You are! Oh, wow, it's great to see you again! It's been so long since our escapades back in Wynn!",
                "cowfusion-drale-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Drale: This is great, actually! I- I can show you around the place! Introduce you to some of the folks we freed together! Oh, what fantastic timing this has been.",
                "cowfusion-drale-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Drale: I just need to figure out which switch to pull... I think it's this one! Probably. I really need to label these things. Alright, here goes!",
                "cowfusion-drale-9",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Drale: Wait, no, that's the wrong-...!", "cowfusion-drale-10", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Drale: Okay. So you are just a regular cow. Not a Woc. Uh... Who let you in, little pal? I'm going to need to have a word about closing the doors...",
                "cowfusion-drale-11",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Drale: Well, this is... awkward. So, then... cow. What's it like being... a cow?",
                "cowfusion-drale-12",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/4] Drale: Right. Okay. Figure I'd best let you go free.", "cowfusion-drale-13", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Drale: ...Unless. Unless. Nobody's... nobody's looking. I could just send you to The Pit... Nobody would know.",
                "cowfusion-drale-14",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Drale: It's... easier this way. It's fine. Maybe you'll even- maybe you'll even make your way out. Good luck, little buddy.",
                "cowfusion-drale-15",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Drale: I, uh... Hah. Very funny. Tell me you're a human, then pretend to be a cow.",
                "cowfusion-drale-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Drale: That's... fine. You know, I'm under quite a lot of stress right now. Working hard, day in and day out. I don't really need your attitude right now!",
                "cowfusion-drale-17",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Drale: You know what? I don't need this attitude. I'm- I'm going to send you to The Pit. Where- where all my other mistakes lie.",
                "cowfusion-drale-18",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Drale: ...You have a weapon. You can probably manage! You don't need anything from me! Here, see how you like it down there!",
                "cowfusion-drale-19",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Drale: ...This doesn't even mean anything! What am I supposed to do with-",
                "cowfusion-drale-20",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/5] Drale: Oh! It's- It's you! Didn't I just...", "cowfusion-drale-21", false);
        s.addSound("[3/5] Drale: ...Um. This is... really awkward, haha. I'm... sorry?", "cowfusion-drale-22", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Drale: You're... the one who pretended to be a cow, right? I, uh... In my defense, I was very stressed. So I dropped you into the Pit.",
                "cowfusion-drale-23",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Drale: ...Anyway! What's- What's going on in your life? Anything interesting?",
                "cowfusion-drale-24",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Drale: Uh... Hm. Maybe- Maybe being a cow is affecting your brain somehow... That can't be good.",
                "cowfusion-drale-25",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Drale: We should get you back to human as quickly as possible. Come on, follow me.",
                "cowfusion-drale-26",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Drale: So... Have you done anything interesting recently? Besides- getting turned into a cow. Obviously.",
                "cowfusion-drale-27",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Drale: You're, uh... Probably wondering what this place is. Just a big city under some random guy's farm, right?",
                "cowfusion-drale-28",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Drale: It's... heh. We've been trying to gather as many of our people as we can. We exiles have to stick together, after all.",
                "cowfusion-drale-29",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Drale: It's a long story. I'm not sure how much of it I really want to tell you, heh. Especially considering... Yeah.",
                "cowfusion-drale-30",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Drale: But. This place is a safe haven for us exiles. A place for us to live until we achieve our goals.",
                "cowfusion-drale-31",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Drale: And- hey! You've seen our secrets now! May as well let it be a safe haven for you as well, right? Heh.",
                "cowfusion-drale-32",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Drale: Oh- the elevator. Here we are. Uh... Just head on in, little buddy? It'll take us up.",
                "cowfusion-drale-33",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Drale: ...You're worrying me. Come on, let's get going. Into the elevator, let's get you back to normal.",
                "cowfusion-drale-34",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Drale: Come on, get in the elevator!", "cowfusion-drale-35", false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Drale: So... here we are. The lab!", "cowfusion-drale-36", false);
        s.addSound("[2/3] Drale: Just... follow me, for now. The machine is this way.", "cowfusion-drale-37", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Drale: There it is! If you step into the machine, real quick, it should... it should work!",
                "cowfusion-drale-38",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Drale: Come on! Just... pop yourself back in the machine!", "cowfusion-drale-39", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Drale: Look at you! As good as new!", "cowfusion-drale-40", false);
        s.addSound("[1/7] Drale: There you are! Back to norm...-", "cowfusion-drale-41", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/7] Drale: soldier?! What are you- that was you the whole time?! Why didn't you tell me!",
                "cowfusion-drale-42",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/7] Drale: Oh gosh, this has been... An awful reunion. I can't believe I dropped you into the Pit...",
                "cowfusion-drale-43",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/7] Drale: I'm so sorry for- for all of that. You should have told me! Oh...",
                "cowfusion-drale-44",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/7] Drale: Okay, uh... Here, take this. As- as compensation for- for all of that.",
                "cowfusion-drale-45",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/7] Drale: I... I need to get back to work. But- uh, if you ever want, feel free to visit sometime? You'll be able to use the entrance at Ranol's farm.",
                "cowfusion-drale-46",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/7] Drale: Maybe I can tell you more about what I've been up to! Heh...",
                "cowfusion-drale-47",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Drale: I am talking to a cow. Again. Why is this where my life has taken me.",
                "cowfusion-drale-48",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Drale: So! What's... going on, little buddy? Any- any souvenirs? From the Pit...?",
                "cowfusion-drale-49",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Drale: Yep. Just a cow...", "cowfusion-drale-50", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Drale: Well, alright. Let's just- get you in my machine, I guess. It worked for the exiles, so maybe it'll work for you..?",
                "cowfusion-drale-51",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Drale: ...Don't look at me like that. Come on, let's get going.", "cowfusion-drale-52", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Drale: Oh, you- Oh. Right! Okay. I don't- I don't quite understand why you would pretend to be a cow. But alright!",
                "cowfusion-drale-53",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Drale: So, uh... Human turned into a cow. Okay. How did you manage to get yourself stuck as a cow, anyway? I didn't think we had anything that could do that...",
                "cowfusion-drale-54",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Drale: My machine. It's- It's not even supposed to do that! I designed it to turn exiles back into Wocs, how would it have...",
                "cowfusion-drale-55",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Drale: Great. Of course it'd have that issue, and just when I thought I...",
                "cowfusion-drale-56",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Drale: Right. Right. Alright. We can work with this! Let's just take you back to that machine, put you in it, and see if it turns you back to normal!",
                "cowfusion-drale-57",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Drale: It'll work. Probably. I mean, I haven't ever tried it, so I can't really say for sure... Oh, yep, you're still here. Let's get moving.",
                "cowfusion-drale-58",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/8] Drale: So... Hey there, little... cow?", "cowfusion-drale-59", false);
        s.addSound("[2/8] Drale: Uh. Do you- do you understand what I'm saying?", "cowfusion-drale-60", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/8] Drale: ...This is stupid. I'm talking to a cow. Of course you can't...",
                "cowfusion-drale-61",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/8] Drale: Well, I guess I could- talk at you. For a bit. If that's, heh, fine with you!",
                "cowfusion-drale-62",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/8] Drale: It's been tough, recently. Working towards a goal that I know is important, but still feels... out of reach.",
                "cowfusion-drale-63",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/8] Drale: And it doesn't seem like anybody else can see that! That this is important! They look at me like I'm going crazy, and-",
                "cowfusion-drale-64",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/8] Drale: I'm not. I know I'm not. We need to find the ship. If we don't, who knows what...",
                "cowfusion-drale-65",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Drale: Anyway! Here's the elevator! Just step on in, and we can head on up to the laboratory.",
                "cowfusion-drale-66",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Drale: Hrrgh- You're- you're not a cow?! Why were you... I just said all that, and you could...",
                "cowfusion-drale-67",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Drale: D-don't worry about the door. It's... It's nothing. Maintenance. That- that's what it is.",
                "cowfusion-drale-68",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Drale: Er... Come on, into the elevator! You want to get back to normal, right? Besides, you'd need a key to get in there, and I don't know where you'd find one of those, haha!",
                "cowfusion-drale-69",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Drale: ...Moo. Yep. I agree. Come on, let's get going. Into the elevator.",
                "cowfusion-drale-70",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Drale: Hm... Oh, hi! Welcome back to my office!", "cowfusion-drale-71", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Drale: Oh, this is- Oh! You're alive! I, ah- heh. Sorry about... all that. I really, really need to label these levers properly...",
                "cowfusion-drale-72",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Drale: Right! Right. You've seen... all that down there, then. I just hope you won't think less of me for it.",
                "cowfusion-drale-73",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Drale: I can... I can tell you more about it later. I hope it wasn't too bad? Down there? You seem to have gotten out in one piece, so...",
                "cowfusion-drale-74",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Drale: ...Oh. Right. Gosh, how long has it been since I-...", "cowfusion-drale-75", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Drale: Okay. Alright, yes, I'll give them better positions. And I'll- I don't know. Apologize. Give them a bonus.",
                "cowfusion-drale-76",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Drale: It's been... hard, recently. We've been working to get back home, and I guess I just... Put too much of myself into that. It's fine! Don't- Don't worry about me.",
                "cowfusion-drale-77",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Drale: Oh. Right, your body! I can fix that! We just need to get back to the machine, and... Poof. You'll be back to normal!",
                "cowfusion-drale-78",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Drale: ...I hope. Hey, being a cow isn't so bad! If- If it doesn't work, we can make you a home here...?",
                "cowfusion-drale-79",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Drale: Uh... It'll work. I'm sure it will work. It's always- always worked in the past! Heh...",
                "cowfusion-drale-80",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/4] Drale: Anyway! Let's get going!", "cowfusion-drale-81", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/7] Drale: So... How have you been? It's been a while since our adventure at Katoa Ranch, hasn't it?",
                "cowfusion-drale-82",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/7] Drale: Well, you've been turned into a cow... Obviously... But besides that!",
                "cowfusion-drale-83",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/7] Drale: Me? Well... heh. I've been doing pretty well, all things considered. We've been gathering exiles from all over the province! Set up a city to hold us all while we work towards...",
                "cowfusion-drale-84",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/7] Drale: It's a long story. I can't tell you everything- not yet. But... All of us here, we don't belong here. We just want to go home.",
                "cowfusion-drale-85",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/7] Drale: And- and maybe if we can find our ship again, we'll be able to prove that we're not irredeemable. That whatever we went through- that it won't define us.",
                "cowfusion-drale-86",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/7] Drale: ...Heh. Don't- don't worry about it too much. For now, this place is enough of a safe haven for us. It'll have to be enough until we succeed.",
                "cowfusion-drale-87",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/7] Drale: We're so close. I can feel it. Just... Just a little while left to go.",
                "cowfusion-drale-88",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Drale: Anyway, uh... Here's the elevator! Just step on in, and it'll take us back to the laboratory.",
                "cowfusion-drale-89",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Drale: The- oh. Uh... It's nothing. Nothing to worry about.", "cowfusion-drale-90", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Drale: It just leads to... maintenance. Yep! Just- just maintenance. Nothing else.",
                "cowfusion-drale-91",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Drale: Into the elevator now, come on! You need a key to get in anyway, and I definitely don't have one laying around!",
                "cowfusion-drale-92",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Drale: ...You're worrying me, friend. Come on, let's get going. Into the elevator, let's get you back to normal.",
                "cowfusion-drale-93",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Drale: Heh... Well, there you are! Good as new! I hope...", "cowfusion-drale-94", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Drale: And- to, uh, compensate you for... you know... Here! One liquid emerald. I feel terrible for how our reunion ended up going... I hope you won't hold it against me?",
                "cowfusion-drale-95",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Drale: Uh... I really should get back to work. But- hey! Feel free to visit whenever you want! You'll be able to use the entrance at Ranol's farm.",
                "cowfusion-drale-96",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Drale: Maybe I can tell you more about what I've been up to! That'd be nice.",
                "cowfusion-drale-97",
                false);

        // Mixed Feelings
        s.addSound("[1/3] Javen: Mo'in lad! We don't get many Wynn folks round 'ere.", "mixedfeelings-javen-1", false);
