        // Beyond the grave
        s.addSound(
                "[1/7] Irlok: Welcome to Bantisu Temple, traveler. We guide lost souls onwards, be they wandering men to town or spirits unable to exit the canyon.",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/7] Irlok: However, recently our job has become much more difficult. The canyon shakes, and changes. Often, long-buried creatures are released as the walls shift.",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/7] Irlok: And unfortunately, the worst has come to pass, that one of these creatures is hostile. The Bantisu monks of old collapsed the entrance to its cave to seal it away...",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/7] Irlok: ...but the rubble has shifted, and the cave is open once more. We were not strong enough to defeat it then, and we are not strong enough to defeat it now.",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/7] Irlok: Even trying to collapse the cave again has ended in failure, for the beast, Krolton, slays our mages and demolitionists in but an instant.",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/7] Irlok: However, the word on the wind tells tales of humans doing the impossible as a matter of rote. Krolton must be dealt with before it leaves the cave- I beg your assistance!",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/7] Irlok: We've no time to spare. I will prepare a short spell to bring you to the cave- Please, wait outside, and prepare yourself.",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Irlok: I apologize for the suddenness of this, but you must understand the urgency. We have no way of knowing when Krolton may emerge.",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Irlok: We will pray for your safety, and that your spirit will not become among those we must guide out of the canyon.",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-9",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/3] Irlok: Now, hold tight, and godspeed!!", "beyondthegrave-irlok-10", false);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Death: IT SEEMS I HAVE A NEW GUEST. WELCOME.", "beyondthegrave-death-1", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Death: MAKE YOURSELF COMFORTABLE. YOU'LL BE STAYING HERE FOR A WHILE.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-2",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Death: NOTHING IS STOPPING YOU FROM TAKING A LOOK AROUND. DON'T TOUCH ANYTHING THOUGH. AND TAKE OFF YOUR SHOES AS YOU ENTER.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-3",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Death: WHEN YOU FEEL LIKE IT, COME TO MY OFFICE UPSTAIRS. WE HAVE A LENGTHY TALK TO HAVE.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-4",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Death: IMPRESSIVE. HOWEVER, THAT WAS SIMPLY ROUND 1, OUT OF 20. EACH ONE WILL BE PROGRESSIVELY MORE DIFFICULT THAN THE LAST. READY?",
                "beyondthegrave-death-5",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Death: ...AH, THE LOOK ON YOUR FACE. PRICELESS. GIVEN MY SKULL IS SOLID AND CANNOT EMOTE, I HAVE TO GET MY FILL OF MAKING FACES SOMEHOW.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-6",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Death: I AM SATISFIED, AND THAT'S ALL I REALLY WANTED FROM YOU.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-7",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Death: NOW AS IS TYPICAL FOR WINNING A QUIZ GAME AGAINST A METAPHYSICAL ENTITY, I WILL DESTROY A WINDOW WITH A CANNONBALL SO YOU MAY GO ANY TIME.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-8",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Death: A TECHNOLOGICAL MARVEL- THE SCREEN TURNS OFF WHEN A GUEST RUDELY LEAVES IN THE MIDDLE OF A GAMESHOW. A NICHE FUNCTION, TO BE SURE, BUT A USEFUL ONE.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-9",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Death: THESE HOURGLASSES SHOW THE LIFESPAN OF HUMANS. WHEN ALL THE SAND HITS THE BOTTOM, I GET A NEW GUEST.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-10",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Death: OH LOOK, HERE'S YOURS. IT SAYS YOU'VE BEEN HERE 126 TIMES IN THE LAST THREE MONTHS. SORRY, 127 NOW.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-11",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Death: MY MIND MUST HAVE SLIPPED, I FORGOT TO MENTION THE MASSIVE HOURGLASS. IT SHOWS HOW MUCH TIME THE WORLD HAS LEFT.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-12",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Death: I'LL GIVE YOU TIME TO GET OVER WHAT YOU HAVE WITNESSED.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-13",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Death: I SUGGEST YOU DON'T EAT ANYTHING THAT YOU ARE SERVED HERE, I HEARD IT IS TO DIE FOR.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-14",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Death: IF I HAD BOUGHT ANY WHEAT THIS MORNING, I'D OFFER A BISCUIT AS CONSOLATION FOR DYING.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-15",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Death: IT'S A SHAME, REALLY. I'M TOLD I MAKE THE BEST LITTLE CHOCOLATE CHIP ONES.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-16",
                true);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Death: FEET OFF THE TABLE PLEASE.", "beyondthegrave-death-17", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Death: IF ANYONE ASKS, YES, I AM MARRIED. JUST BECAUSE I DON'T HAVE A HEART DOESN'T MEAN THAT I CAN'T LOVE.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-18",
                true);
        s.addSound("[1/2] Death: THIS IS AN EMPTY ROOM.", "beyondthegrave-death-19", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Death: AROUND THE MANSION, THERE ARE MANY MORE EMPTY ROOMS.", "beyondthegrave-death-20", true);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Death: THIS IS MY OFFICE. GUESS WHAT I DO HERE. HUH?", "beyondthegrave-death-21", false);
        s.addSound("[2/4] Death: I DIE OF BOREDOM.", "beyondthegrave-death-22", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Death: ...REALLY? NOTHING? YOU HUMANS HAVE NO SENSE OF HUMOUR.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-23",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/4] Death: PLEASE TAKE A SEAT. LET'S REVIEW YOUR OPTIONS.", "beyondthegrave-death-24", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Death: THIS IS THE LIBRARY, WHERE MY GUESTS COME TO SPEND THEIR TIME.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-25",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Death: FEEL FREE TO TAKE YOUR TIME AND READ UP. KNOWLEDGE IS POWER, AND ALL THAT.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-26",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Death: YOU COULD READ ALL OF THEM IF YOU LIKE, BUT THEY ARE ALL IN LATIN, AND I HEARD THAT IS NOW A DEAD LAGUAGE.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-27",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Death: IT SEEMS YOU REALLY WANTED TO KNOW WHAT WAS BEHIND THIS DOOR.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-28",
                true);
        s.addSound("[2/4] Death: I GUESS YOU WILL GET WHAT YOU WANTED...", "beyondthegrave-death-29", true);
        s.addSound("[3/4] Death: ANOTHER DOOR.", "beyondthegrave-death-30", true);
        s.addSound("[4/4] Death: DO YOU REALLY THINK IT WAS WORTH YOUR TIME?", "beyondthegrave-death-31", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Death: IF YOU HEAR SCREAMING, DON'T WORRY. IT'S JUST THE WALLS.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-32",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Death: IS MY MANSION SO DULL YOU WOULD RATHER GO ROCK CLIMBING?",
                "beyondthegrave-death-33",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Death: I'VE HEARD THERE IS SOME GUY AT THE TOP OF SOME ICE TOWER RIPPING ME OFF.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-34",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Death: THIS BOOK IS SO BAD, EVEN THE LONG-WINDED AND PAINFUL DEATH OF SWEENEY S. GREENVILLE IS BETTER THAN THIS.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-35",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Death: THE REMOTE'S FIDDLY. YOU NEED TO BE SITTING ON THE COUCH FOR IT TO WORK.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-36",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/14] Death: I KNOW THIS SEEMS LIKE AN ODD PLACE TO BE. SITTING IN FRONT OF DEATH.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-37",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/14] Death: THE TRUTH IS, YOU HAVE BEEN HERE MANY TIMES BEFORE.", "beyondthegrave-death-38", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/14] Death: THE CATCH IS, A MORTAL MAY NEVER BE ALLOWED TO SPEAK OF MY REALM.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-39",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/14] Death: SO I MAKE EVERYONE WHO VISITS...SIMPLY FORGET.", "beyondthegrave-death-40", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/14] Death: IT'S EASIER ON EVERYONE THAT WAY. YOU WOULDN'T WANT TO TELL PEOPLE ABOUT YOUR DEATH, THAT WOULD BE WEIRD.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-41",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/14] Death: THIS TIME, HOWEVER, I'LL JUST HAVE TO LET YOU REMEMBER YOUR JOURNEY HERE.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-42",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/14] Death: WHY YOU ASK? OH, YOU WOULDN'T WANT TO FORGET THE JOURNEY OF A LIFETIME, RIGHT?",
                "beyondthegrave-death-43",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/14] Death: THAT, AND I RECEIVED SOME POSTAGE, SHALL WE SAY. SOMEONE IS INVESTED IN YOUR CONTINUED SURVIVAL.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-44",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[9/14] Death: I ALWAYS ALLOW PEOPLE THE OPPORTUNITY TO RE-ENTER THE MORTAL PLANE ANYWAY.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-45",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/14] Death: CALL IT BARGAINING WITH DEATH IF YOU LIKE. TRUTH IS, I JUST GET A BIT BORED.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-46",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[11/14] Death: IF YOU WISH TO RETURN TO LIFE, AND I CAN NEVER UNDERSTAND WHY PEOPLE DO, ALL YOU HAVE TO DO IS BEAT THAT WHICH SENT YOU HERE.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-47",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[12/14] Death: IN YOUR CASE, IT IS THE CREATURE KNOWN AS KROLTON. I SIMPLY ASK YOU SPEND A BIT OF TIME HERE AND PLAY A SHORT GAME BEFORE YOU GO, IN THE OTHER UPSTAIRS ROOM.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-48",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[13/14] Death: I DO ENJOY MY CHATS WITH HUMANS, THEY NEVER SAY ANYTHING.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-49",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[14/14] Death: WHICH IS ODD, BECAUSE OUT OF THE TWO OF US, THEY ARE THE ONES WITH VOCAL CHORDS.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-50",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Death: SOMETHING I'M FINDING INCREASINGLY ANNOYING IS HOW MANY PEOPLE ARE FINDING WAYS TO BECOME IMMORTAL NOWADAYS. INTELLIGENT COMPANY IS STARTING TO GET A BIT SCARCER.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-51",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Death: OH, YOU ARE STILL HERE. IF YOU WANT TO LEAVE, I SIMPLY WANT A BIT OF ENTERTAINMENT BEFORE YOU DO. WOULD YOU GO TO THE GAME ROOM ON THE OTHER END OF THE MANSION?",
                "beyondthegrave-death-52",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/5] Death: WELL, I SEE YOU ARE LEAVING.", "beyondthegrave-death-53", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Death: IT WAS NICE TO HAVE YOU BACK AGAIN, I DO ENJOY YOUR VISITS.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-54",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Death: TO RISE BACK TO LIFE, YOU MUST DEFEAT THE ONE WHO BROUGHT YOU TO MY HANDS.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-55",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Death: YOU'VE MANAGED IT BEFORE SO I CAN'T SEE WHY YOU CAN'T MANAGE IT AGAIN. AFTERALL, YOU MANAGE TO KEEP DYING.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-56",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Death: ...OR YOU KNOW, DON'T. I DO ENJOY HAVING A LITTLE COLOUR AROUND THE MANSION.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-57",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Death: ...AND ANOTHER THING. GIVEN WHAT I SAID EARLIER, IT FEELS RIGHT TO LET YOU KNOW SOMETHING.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-58",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Death: SO LONG AS THE BEAST THAT KILLED YOU DIES BY SOMETHING YOU CAUSE, YOU WILL RETURN TO LIFE. SO BE AS RECKLESS AS YOU WANT.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-59",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Death: AND IF YOU ARE TOO RECKLESS, THAT WILL BE A VALUABLE LESSON TO YOU. SINCE KROLTON HAS NOTICED YOU AGAIN, IâLL LEAVE YOU TO IT.",
                "beyondthegrave-death-60",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Irlok: Oh, thank goodness. You've returned- not free of wear, but certainly alive. Did you need to flee from Krolton, or is he...?",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-11",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/6] Irlok: Truly? The beast is dead?", "beyondthegrave-irlok-12", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Irlok: Gracious, I don't think I've ever been so relieved. Krolton was responsible for thousands of deaths long ago. You've prevented an oncoming massacre!",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Irlok: Bantisu Temple owes you a great deal. Here, then- a suitable reward.",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-14",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Irlok: A powerful Bantisu artifact, as reward for defeating a beast that menaced in antiquated times.",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-15",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Irlok: Safe travels, human. Whether it was luck or strength that had you prevail, I pray it will not fail you in the future.",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Irlok: We have a job that needs doing, but I'm afraid you're too weak. Come back when you are level 87.",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-17",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Irlok: You are truly an amazing warrior. Thank you for putting an end to Krolton.",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-18",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Irlok: I have written the coordinates of the cave Krolton hides in, in your quest book.",
                "beyondthegrave-irlok-19",
                false);

        // The hidden city
        s.addSound(
                "[1/14] Narder: A human? Agh! Don't worry about getting me medical attention, I've got this under control...",
                "thehiddencity-narder-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/14] Narder: It's a broken leg. I'm already getting it treated, but I have a job to do elsewise- and a time sensitive one, too.",
                "thehiddencity-narder-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/14] Narder: I won't be able to do it like this, but it doesn't matter if I'm the one who carries it out. It just needs to be done.",
                "thehiddencity-narder-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/14] Narder: I don't work for villagers, I was hired to come here by other humans... there's something you must keep secret.",
                "thehiddencity-narder-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/14] Narder: Swear it! If you're going to take the job, and my payment for it, you must be silent about it!",
                "thehiddencity-narder-5",
                false);
        s.addSound("[6/14] Narder: Do you agree?", "thehiddencity-narder-6", false);
        s.addSound("[7/14] Narder: Good. To business then.", "thehiddencity-narder-7", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/14] Narder: There is a hidden town in the canyon here. Up in the mountains- it was built and run by humans.",
                "thehiddencity-narder-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[9/14] Narder: Now, the villagers have very strict rules about humans living in their lands, and it's VERY illegal.",
                "thehiddencity-narder-9",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/14] Narder: I was contacted by the Mayor because he is aware that the town may have become... compromised.",
                "thehiddencity-narder-10",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[11/14] Narder: The job is to figure out who and why, of course. To let this slip could collapse the treatise between our races.",
                "thehiddencity-narder-11",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[12/14] Narder: I've never been to the city in the mountains, but I was given instructions. Here, I'll write down the location in your book.",
                "thehiddencity-narder-12",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[13/14] Narder: Be aware though, they won't let you in unless the area is safe. They can't risk villagers wandering in.",
                "thehiddencity-narder-13",
                false);
        s.addSound("[14/14] Narder: Good luck.", "thehiddencity-narder-14", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Curious Villager: Hm? Oh, a fellow adventurer, I see! I'm sorry, but this discovery is mine to make. There's something strange about that door...",
                "thehiddencity-curiousvillager-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Curious Villager: Deadly gasses? Nonsense! As you can see the two of us are breathing just fine.",
                "thehiddencity-curiousvillager-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Curious Villager: You want me to leave? Why, so that you can have all of the glory for yourself? Ha, not a chance!",
                "thehiddencity-curiousvillager-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Curious Villager: The only way I'm leaving is if I can get that door open or if the whole cave starts crashing down on us.",
                "thehiddencity-curiousvillager-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Curious Villager: Gweh! I just had to go running my mouth about the cave collapsing! I'm out- if you have any sense you'll leave too!",
                "thehiddencity-curiousvillager-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Eltom Guard: Thank you for getting rid of that curious villager! We thought he'd never leave.",
                "thehiddencity-eltomguard-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Eltom Guard: I've never seen you before. Who gave you access to the town?",
                "thehiddencity-eltomguard-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Eltom Guard: You're here in place of the detective the mayor hired?",
                "thehiddencity-eltomguard-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Eltom Guard: Normally, I wouldn't believe that, but come in. We're desperate.",
                "thehiddencity-eltomguard-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Eltom Guard: If you ever need to leave and get back, I can simply open the way.",
                "thehiddencity-eltomguard-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Eltom Guard: You probably should be going now. Our mayor can get impatient.",
                "thehiddencity-eltomguard-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/8] Eoric: What are you doing here? I'm writing an important letter, this better be worth my time.",
                "thehiddencity-eoric-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/8] Eoric: What? Narder sent you? Why'd he send a Ragni soldier?", "thehiddencity-eoric-2", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/8] Eoric: I didn't think the army were authorized to know about Eltom, especially Fruma recruits.",
                "thehiddencity-eoric-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/8] Eoric: Anyway, Eltom's secrecy is in great danger. We have found evidence of a traitor.",
                "thehiddencity-eoric-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/8] Eoric: We have locked down all of the exits. No one leaves or enters without my permission.",
                "thehiddencity-eoric-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/8] Eoric: We need a detective to sniff out the traitor and expose him.",
                "thehiddencity-eoric-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/8] Eoric: Start by asking the citizens around here about anything suspicious they've seen.",
                "thehiddencity-eoric-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/8] Eoric: When you find the culprit, remember to leave him alive! The guards will take care of him.",
                "thehiddencity-eoric-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Reder: Sorry, detective, but I haven't seen anything suspicious. In fact, I haven't even left my house for the last week.",
                "thehiddencity-reder-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Nichye: The only suspicious thing I've seen is a hooded man walking around. There's not many people in Eltom, so it's weird.",
                "thehiddencity-nichye-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sybeth: If you want to find out anything, the best person to ask is Lumilda. She's in her bakery, next to the Scroll Shop.",
                "thehiddencity-sybeth-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Lumilda: Ah, detective! What brings you to the sweet Lumilda's Bakery?",
                "thehiddencity-lumilda-1",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/6] Lumilda: Hm, yes, there is a weird person coming through.", "thehiddencity-lumilda-2", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Lumilda: It's a hooded man. Never seen the face. A trouble maker, if you ask me!",
                "thehiddencity-lumilda-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Lumilda: He's been here a few times, usually writing things on a piece of paper. That man's a real mystery. No one even knows where he lives.",
                "thehiddencity-lumilda-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Lumilda: One time my grandson couldn't resist and followed the man. Last thing he saw was the man leaving through the Eastern Exit.",
                "thehiddencity-lumilda-5",
                false);
        s.addSound("[6/6] Lumilda: Ain't that a place to start, sweetheart?", "thehiddencity-lumilda-6", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] ???: Ah, you must be the detective. None of those half-witted Eltomites could figure it out.",
                "thehiddencity-ardulf-1",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/6] ???: I guess the grook is out of the pen then.", "thehiddencity-ardulf-2", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] ???: This town shouldn't even be here. Humans aren't allowed to settle in Gavel.",
                "thehiddencity-ardulf-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] ???: These humans couldn't be bothered to fight their own war, so they hid an entire city here.",
                "thehiddencity-ardulf-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] ???: Traitor? I'm no traitor. I'm just looking to carry out the law where it needs to be carried out. Nothing personal, yes?",
                "thehiddencity-ardulf-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Ardulf: Maybe they'll actually use âArdulfâ instead of saying âfreakâ once they've seen the good I can do for them!",
                "thehiddencity-ardulf-6",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/5] Hilan: H-h-help!", "thehiddencity-hilan-1", false);
        s.addSound("[2/5] Hilan: Hooded man... Climbed tower...", "thehiddencity-hilan-2", false);
        s.addSound("[3/5] Hilan: Demanded to use a ship... I refused...", "thehiddencity-hilan-3", false);
        s.addSound("[4/5] Hilan: He beat me up... And left...", "thehiddencity-hilan-4", false);
        s.addSound("[5/5] Hilan: Hurry!", "thehiddencity-hilan-5", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Ardulf: What are you doing here? Why are you protecting this illegal town?",
                "thehiddencity-ardulf-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Ardulf: The Villagers will not be happy about Eltom. This could seriously harm the Gavel-Wynn relationship.",
                "thehiddencity-ardulf-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Ardulf: You can't stop me. You wouldn't murder one of your own, would you?",
                "thehiddencity-ardulf-9",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Ardulf: I will tell the mayor of Thesead all about this place, and claim my reward for doing so. I will be rich and if you want to stop me you'll have to do it yourself.",
                "thehiddencity-ardulf-10",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/7] Thesead's Mayor: What brings a human to my office?", "thehiddencity-theseadsmayor-1", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/7] Thesead's Mayor: A letter? Oh, that. The one about Eltom? Don't look so worried. The secret is safe with me.",
                "thehiddencity-theseadsmayor-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/7] Thesead's Mayor: Yes, I know about Eltom. After all, its mayor is my ex-husband.",
                "thehiddencity-theseadsmayor-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/7] Thesead's Mayor: It may seem odd, a love between a villager and a human. I know, but our race did not stop us from being in love.",
                "thehiddencity-theseadsmayor-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/7] Thesead's Mayor: The person who left the letter about Eltom is our son, Ardulf. As soon as Eoric found out about our child, he panicked and left me.",
                "thehiddencity-theseadsmayor-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/7] Thesead's Mayor: Ardulf will never be accepted as a half breed... Still, I hope he's OK.",
                "thehiddencity-theseadsmayor-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/7] Thesead's Mayor: Huh, oh yeah, one more thing. The switch under the table... go on, press it!",
                "thehiddencity-theseadsmayor-7",
                false);

        // Enter the dojo
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sensei Miyagi: Oh hohoho! So a human has found their way to my humble dojo? Intriguing! However, I could not ask you to attempt my training til you were level 89.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/7] Sensei Miyagi: Oh hohoho! So a human has found their way to my humble dojo? Intriguing! I am called Sensei Miyagi. I welcome you.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/7] Sensei Miyagi: This dojo, I have dedicated to honing skills in all of the arts- from martial prowess and mental acuity, to craftsmanship and artistry.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/7] Sensei Miyagi: Many have come- traveled from all corners of the earth to this humble one's dojo to train themselves and grow stronger. I am to presume you are the same?",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/7] Sensei Miyagi: Although, while I have enjoyed my life's work here, I cannot deny I am getting on in years. I seek a successor, a master of many skills to take my place.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/7] Sensei Miyagi: To the one who should master the arts, I would bequeath The Masterâs Gi, a symbol of resolute skill. Of course, do not feel pressured to take over for me, hoho!",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/7] Sensei Miyagi: As long as I may teach others and bring them to new heights, I am satisfied. Whether your aim be merely to sharpen your skills or to allow me to retire, you are welcomed.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/7] Sensei Miyagi: When you are ready to begin, purify yourself in the waters of the spring behind the dojo, and I will guide you to your first challenge.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sensei Miyagi: Whenever you are ready to begin, purify yourself in the waters of the spring behind the dojo.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-9",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Challenger Apprentice: I have been training for years, mastering all of Sensei Miyagi's challenges but one... the physical strength challenge defeats me.",
                "enterthedojo-challengerapprentice-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Challenger Apprentice: I trained for years hoping to achieve the Master's Gi chestplate. All of Sensei Miyagi's challenges come easy for me except for the sight challenge!",
                "enterthedojo-challengerapprentice-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Challenger Apprentice: All of Sensei Miyagi's challenges come as a walk in the park for me, except the abstract tranquility challenge. I one day hope to conquer it and gain the Master's Gi.",
                "enterthedojo-challengerapprentice-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Challenger Apprentice: Alas, after all my training, I can not muster the power to conquer Sensei Miyagi's combat challenge... it is the only challenge that defeats me!",
                "enterthedojo-challengerapprentice-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Challenger Apprentice: I see you have mustered the power to defeat all four challenges. You have my utmost respect.",
                "enterthedojo-challengerapprentice-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Challenger Apprentice: I congratulate you my friend on your success in the challenges, but the real reward in this situation is the experience, not the physical reward!",
                "enterthedojo-challengerapprentice-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Challenger Apprentice: I congratulate you on your recent success regarding the four challenges. I envy you and your success.",
                "enterthedojo-challengerapprentice-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sensei Miyagi: Here we are then- The ââ¤âââ¡ Room. Here tests your agility! Even these old bones can scale this room in short order- How shall you fare?",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-10",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Sensei Miyagi: I recognize your skill, and you have passed the challenge of the ââ¤âââ¡ Room! Hoho, but the next challenge has defeated many an apprentice.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-11",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Sensei Miyagi: Now, comes the ââââ£â Room! Here, your combat prowess shall be put to the test. Martial skill comes easily to me...but what of your own?",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-12",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Sensei Miyagi: I hear many things about human combat skill, so I believe I shall watch this challenge myself. Enter now, challenger!",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sensei Miyagi: Defeat the dummies, and bring their tokens to the door! Simple, yes?",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-14",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sensei Miyagi: Show no fear, challenger! There is no shame in failing.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-15",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sensei Miyagi: And worry not, the ââââ£â Room is reinforced against all manner of attacks. Run wild, hoho!",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sensei Miyagi: It is fascinating to see how you battle. Very different from my stylings!",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-17",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Sensei Miyagi: And I am to recognize your combat skill, and proclaim your passage of the ââââ£â Room. Well done!",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-18",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Sensei Miyagi: Next, however, is not a challenge of physical skill, but of observation and logical reasoning, in this- the ââââ¢â£â Room. Here, a puzzle awaits.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-19",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Sensei Miyagi: You must discern the path in order to bring the red block to the gold block. Simple in theory...complex in practice, as are many things.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-20",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Sensei Miyagi: Remember this as you work- Change your perspective, and the reality changes.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-21",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Sensei Miyagi: And there, I recognize your mental acuity! You have passed the ââââ¢â£â Room. You are doing quite well, but many have gotten to this point and had a single point stymie them.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-22",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Sensei Miyagi: Welcome then, to the last challenge I offer you, held within the â¢ââ£âââââ Room and cavern.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-23",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Sensei Miyagi: Your task here, is to become tranquil, and at peace with nature. What that entails... I leave up to you.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-24",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Sensei Miyagi: There are many paths to tranquility. Whatever you choose, you will know when you have reached the point of success.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-25",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/7] Sensei Miyagi: I see it now. The troubled heart you came here with is troubled no longer. I recognize your mastery of the â¢ââ£âââââ Room.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-26",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/7] Sensei Miyagi: Oh hoho... It is just like a human to do what cannot be done. That is each challenge of my humble dojo, completed!",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-27",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/7] Sensei Miyagi: So! While I did advise you not to feel pressured of it, I am curious, young master. Do you wish to take my place here, so I may sit these old bones down?",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-28",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/7] Sensei Miyagi: ...Ah, of course not. Despite your mastery, this is merely a single step on your journey. Needn't worry, I understand completely.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-29",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/7] Sensei Miyagi: I am certain that I will find a suitable successor before my time comes- and equally as certain that I've many a year to go, hoho!",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-30",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/7] Sensei Miyagi: Nevertheless, you have completed the challenges of this humble Sensei, and as such, I will provide you what was promised.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-31",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/7] Sensei Miyagi: Wear this [Master's Gi] with pride, and remember this final lesson- There is never a point in life that you will stop learning. See the world and its lessons every day of your life, young master.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-32",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sensei Miyagi: Hoho... Yes, this old man still has plenty of life left in him. Do not waste the gifts you have, young master.",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-33",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sensei Miyagi: Of course, you wield a weapon to battle, so of course it is different from unarmed combat, hoho...",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-34",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sensei Miyagi: Perhaps you may be interested in learning to fight unarmed after!",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-35",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sensei Miyagi: Oh, this is getting quite good. I should get a snack to eat while I watch...",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-36",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sensei Miyagi: Hmhm, I'll be right back! Continue fighting- And do not worry if you finish before I return! I will be quick!",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-37",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sensei Miyagi: Ahh, there we are. Now come on, addled old brain of mine, where were we...",
                "enterthedojo-senseimiyagi-38",
                false);

        // Fantastic Voyage
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Relend: You don't seem very mighty, come back when you're level 90!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Relend: Let's go, just you and me! On a fantastic voyage across the sea!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Relend: We'll go in search of a long-lost island, old chap! And here I have the guidance map!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Relend: The map, oh so grand! Why, I have it here in my hand!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Relend: It's the map to a magical place! I sure hope it doesn't vanish without a tra-",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Relend: Good grief! That raucous parrot is such a little thief!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Relend: If we are to explore the ocean blue, that parrot you surely must pursue!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Relend: Get on it then, no time for a  nap! That thieving parrot has our map!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Relend: Perhaps these citizens may help us out, ask them about the parrot's route!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-9",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Jofash Resident: Hey-o, human! What can I do for ya?", "fantasticvoyage-breadman-1", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Jofash Resident: What can I do for you?", "fantasticvoyage-breadman-2", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Jofash Resident: Oh, you know me, pal, just doin' the rounds.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Jofash Resident: Waterin' the pots, starin' at the water, potterin' the sta-",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-4",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/3] Jofash Resident: ...wait, scratch that last one.", "fantasticvoyage-breadman-5", false);
        s.addSound("[1/99] Jofash Resident: You know what, I'm glad you asked.", "fantasticvoyage-breadman-6", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/99] Jofash Resident: Lots of people these days are going crazy for that 'all-natural, multiple grains, bred ethically' garbage.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/99] Jofash Resident: Really, I wish I could see those nutters sit down and take a good bite of some raw, authentic Rye, or a hearty whole-wheat.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/99] Jofash Resident: That's the stuff that puts hairs on your chest, my pappy used to say. Good, strong, proper bread from out in the fields.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-9",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/99] Jofash Resident: We used to be farmers, you know. Out near Maltic. WHEW! Glad I moved here though! Not so many places serve better rum than good ol' Jofash!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-10",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/99] Jofash Resident: Back to the point at hand, though, bread. Man oh man I feel like I could go on forever about this.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-11",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/99] Jofash Resident: You know what people always miss when discussing bread, the CONSISTENCY! The consistency is consistently the most im-",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-12",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/99] Jofash Resident: Oh, haha, 'consistently,' didn't even mean to do that. Heheh...",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[9/99] Jofash Resident: Ah, there you are! The ol' train of thought gets derailed sometimes, you see.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-14",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/99] Jofash Resident: But I can tell that you're a real enthusiast for bread!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-15",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[11/99] Jofash Resident: Back to the topic at hand! Consistency! The consistency is consistently the most important part of any good loaf.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[12/99] Jofash Resident: Overusin' so-called 'refined' grains is a sure and done way to get runny slop that's not fit for the pigs.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-17",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[13/99] Jofash Resident: Come to think, you shouldn't feed pig refined grains anyway. It's hard on their digestion.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-18",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[14/99] Jofash Resident: Of course! Digestion. A topic I'll get to later!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-19",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[15/99] Jofash Resident: Anyway, whole grains are where the money's at! I'd swear it on these plants.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-20",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[16/99] Jofash Resident: What you want is a thick-crusted, chewy loaf that you can savor! Not some frail morsel that collapses under its own weight. Why, the things I've seen...",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-21",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[17/99] Jofash Resident: In particular, have you seen some of the scraps sold at Ahmsord? Ridiculous!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-22",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[18/99] Jofash Resident: I'll let you in on a little secret. The Sky's Kitchen's great and all, but what passes for bread there is intolerable. No substance at all!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-23",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[19/99] Jofash Resident: What you'll want to do is get it straight from the fields, right from the soil! Well, not literally, but from the countryside! Leave breadmakin' to those who've been workin' with grain before they could even walk on two legs!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-24",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[20/99] Jofash Resident: Heck, I bet even I could do a better job than those snobby sauciers.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-25",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[21/99] Jofash Resident: Right. Digestion. The fiber in whole-grain bread is a real lifesaver.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-26",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[22/99] Jofash Resident: Did you know that whole-grain bread has four times the fiber of white bread? Now you do!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-27",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[23/99] Jofash Resident: Helps keep you full and fit. Want to avoid lookin' like a loaf of white bread yourself? Fiber's your man.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-28",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[24/99] Jofash Resident: Nothin' beats a rich, fresh-ground fresh-baked loaf with a slab of flat-iron steak. Red meat and fiber makes a real man, as my pappy once said.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-29",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[25/99] Jofash Resident: Oh, how time flies. Where was I? Right, white bread.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-30",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[26/99] Jofash Resident: That stuff's poison, I tell you! Not a lick of nutritional value!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-31",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[27/99] Jofash Resident: It's more milk and sugar than bread! Hardly somethin' you'd want to eat, never mind something for which you'd pay extra!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-32",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[28/99] Jofash Resident: Those hawkers can pretend that it's an upper-crust good all they want, but we all know it's just a waste of dough.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-33",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[29/99] Jofash Resident: Heheh, I did it again! Sorry, sorry, I'll get the train back on track. Heh...",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-34",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[30/99] Jofash Resident: Blendin' grains? Why jumble the flavors and textures? Just make two loaves of bread instead of one! Or several, if we're talkin' about more than two types of grain.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-35",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[31/99] Jofash Resident: Say, that reminds me! Bread's probably the most versatile food. You can make it from just about any type of grain.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-36",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[32/99] Jofash Resident: But just because you can doesn't mean that you should. Who could stomach somethin' like 'Oatmeal-Bran Fusion Delight'? WHO WOULD EVEN MAKE BREAD OUT OF OATS?!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-37",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[33/99] Jofash Resident: Just a waste of food, in my opinion. Sure, it may be the hottest new culinary sensation now, but it'll die out like any other idiotic fad in just days. I'm positive that nobody's eatin' it for the taste, that's for sure. Like 'Seven Colors of the Grainbow,' or 'Hearty Hemp-tastic,' or...",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-38",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[34/99] Jofash Resident: ...and don't get me started on 'Pain au Cinfras'! But really, Oatmeal-Bran Fusion Delight is among the worst. Oh! That reminds me about a better use for oats.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-39",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[35/99] Jofash Resident: If you want to avoid bein' three sheets to the wind after a busy night of Jofash Rum, then eat a hearty bowl of oatmeal.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-40",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[36/99] Jofash Resident: Sounds crazy, I know. But it actually works. Take it from me; I've tried it!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-41",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[37/99] Jofash Resident: While anythin' made of grain helps, oats are particularly good at this.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-42",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[38/99] Jofash Resident: And I'd bet my bread that you'd rather eat oatmeal than Oatmeal-Bran Fusion Delight, whatever that's supposed to be.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-43",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[39/99] Jofash Resident: Though it seems like you just can't get a good loaf of bread nearby. Sure, there's sailin' biscuits, but that hardly qualifies!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-44",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[40/99] Jofash Resident: I can't stomach the fancy stuff, so I just make my own. Not only is it cheaper, but it also tastes much better.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-45",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[41/99] Jofash Resident: It isn't too difficult. Besides the obvious, you'll just need some salt and yeast. Grab something to write with, y'hear? Take some notes!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-46",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[42/99] Jofash Resident: Ready? Right, let's get started! The less ingredients you use, the closer you'll get to makin' a real loaf! Not the wannabe poundcakes eaten by wannabe spendthrifts.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-47",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[43/99] Jofash Resident: There's a common misconception that you need sugar for yeast to start risin'. Not true!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-48",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[44/99] Jofash Resident: Give it some time, and bread without sugar will rise just as well. If you want somethin' good, you need to put in the time and effort for it!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-49",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[45/99] Jofash Resident: Get it right, and you'll have the perfect taste and texture for nothin' more than a few hours of your time!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-50",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[46/99] Jofash Resident: Let me make it clear: you don't want sugar in your bread. It'll do a number on its taste and your teeth.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-51",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[47/99] Jofash Resident: I'll cover the taste first. The sugar fights with the raw, savory flavors of an otherwise respectable loaf of bread.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-52",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[48/99] Jofash Resident: It also fights with your teeth. Bread's quite sticky as it is, and the sugar doesn't do it any favors.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-53",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[49/99] Jofash Resident: Why, I can still remember the time that I got a cavity. Cried my eyes out, I did.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-54",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[50/99] Jofash Resident: Eventually, my pappy had enough, and he went for the ol' string-on-a-doorknob trick. He got me good there, though it took him a few tries.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-55",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[51/99] Jofash Resident: Ah, it seems like I got distracted. Back to the topic at hand.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-56",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[52/99] Jofash Resident: You aren't goin' to get quite as much of an effect on your digestion than coarse-ground whole-grain bread. It keeps most of the fiber intact, after all.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-57",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[53/99] Jofash Resident: You know how fruit juice contains next to no fiber because none of it goes into the juice? It's the same deal with white bread.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-58",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[54/99] Jofash Resident: Fruit juice was banned in my household. As my pappy liked to say, a real man only drinks hard spirits and the sweat runnin' down his face! Though I wasn't allowed to have the former, not yet at least! Heheh! So I drank milk instead.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-59",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[55/99] Jofash Resident: Say, if you haven't done so already, try bread dipped in milk! Go on! There's nothin' quite like it. Don't accidentally drop the bread into the milk, of course.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-60",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[56/99] Jofash Resident: You'll end up with a bloated mess with the consistency of a sponge. And you should know by now that consistency is everythin'!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-61",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[57/99] Jofash Resident: While we're on the subject of milk, do you know how some folks can't drink it? Oh, yes, they can try, but sooner or later their belly will protest.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-62",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[58/99] Jofash Resident: It's the same deal with bread! Stick with whole-grain, nothin' added. That way, you don't have to worry about surprise milk appearances and whatnot.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-63",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[59/99] Jofash Resident: You got that? Let me know when you're ready for more. Say, you know what? I oughta talk a bit slower to help you digest what I'm sayin'. Oh! 'Digest'! I did it again! Heheh...",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-64",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[60/99] Jofash Resident: Right, then, somethin' that really peeves me is people who use bakin' powder. What's wrong with some good ol' yeast?",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-65",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[61/99] Jofash Resident: Too little of it, and it'll go plum flat in the oven. Just a little too much of it, and your bread's goin' to be as bitter as wormwood!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-66",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[62/99] Jofash Resident: The only way to get a size that's just right is the long way! Wait until the yeast works its magic, and bake it right as it reaches a good size.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-67",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[63/99] Jofash Resident: There's also nothin' quite like the smell of yeast as it causes the dough to rise! Works up quite the appetite, it does.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-68",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[64/99] Jofash Resident: Some people put the cart before the horse and think that yeast works like bakin' powder. Try that, and you'll end up with some scorchin'-hot bricks in your oven.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-69",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[65/99] Jofash Resident: No, you have to do it right, and doin' it right means leavin' some of the work to the yeast.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-70",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[66/99] Jofash Resident: Unless you like flat breads. I can't see why anyone would, though. Bread's supposed to be puffy and chewy, not some dough jerky!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-71",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[67/99] Jofash Resident: Though that may not be the case for some other pastries. For one, I've never once heard of a pie with a chewy crust.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-72",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[68/99] Jofash Resident: Really, the beauty in bread lies with its simplicity! No complicated steps, no chances for the dough to rebel. Certainly not as fickle as somethin' like a cream puff.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-73",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[69/99] Jofash Resident: If you treat the dough with respect, the bread will respect you in turn. It's simple stuff, really! No finnickin' around with stiff peaks, or needin' half a dozen bowls to mix in, or getting a flaky dough just right, or...",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-74",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[70/99] Jofash Resident: ...and not to mention that just about everythin' needs butter in some shape or form! Really, what's with it? It's not like the stuff grows on trees!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-75",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[71/99] Jofash Resident: Makin' the pastry shiny. Makin' it taste rich. Makin' the dough thick. There's no end to it! Bread's so much simpler to handle.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-76",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[72/99] Jofash Resident: Though some people insist on putin' butter in the bread. Not just on it, but in it! There's more butter than bread at that point!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-77",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[73/99] Jofash Resident: I don't have anythin' against butter itself, mind you. It's great on toast! Just I think that it oughta stay on the toast rather than in it.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-78",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[74/99] Jofash Resident: Not to mention there's a time, place, and occasion for it. If you put butter on everythin, you're goin' to get sick of it real quickly. Eat it in moderation! Your tongue and your emerald pouch will thank you.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-79",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[75/99] Jofash Resident: Of course, there's always margarine, but why settle for somethin' inferior? You shouldn't settle for anythin' less than the quality you'd expect from your bread!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-80",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[76/99] Jofash Resident: Though, now that I look at it, bread does get a reputation for bein' a breakfast food. That's ridiculous! It's got a place in every meal of the day!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-81",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[77/99] Jofash Resident: Sandwiches? They've got bread in 'em. Casseroles? Any respectable one has it as a shell. Bread sticks? It's in the name, for cryin' out loud!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-82",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[78/99] Jofash Resident: Done right, and it's also great as a side. I already mentioned havin' a fresh-ground fresh-baked loaf of hole grain with a slab of flat-iron steak, but really, a well-sliced loaf and some dippin butter can transform a family dinner into a banquet!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-83",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[79/99] Jofash Resident: They're almost as versatile as potatoes! Actually, even more so, I'd say!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-84",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[80/99] Jofash Resident: As my pappy liked to say, a real man's got to earn his daily bread through his own toilin'. As you can see, I've taken his advice to heart!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-85",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[81/99] Jofash Resident: ...I feel that I'm missin' somethin' important that I wanted to discuss. Hang on for a bit, would you?",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-86",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[82/99] Jofash Resident: Ah, of course! I can't believe that I forgot! I wanted to cover some thoughts about bread consistency.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-87",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[83/99] Jofash Resident: Namely, the two extremes: too chewy and not chewy enough. I already spoke on hardly chewy bread plenty, but there's such a thing as too much of a good thing.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-88",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[84/99] Jofash Resident: And in this case, bread chewiness is the good thing. You don't want your bread to be too chewy, got it?",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-89",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[85/99] Jofash Resident: Too chewy's a step right towards bread that's outright rubbery. Your teeth'll bounce right off it!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-90",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[86/99] Jofash Resident: Sure, too much give in the dough's awkward and sets you up for bitin' your own tongue, but too firm of a loaf can lead to much of the same.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-91",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[87/99] Jofash Resident: They always say never to bite off more than you can chew, but you oughta be careful not to bite off any less than that, either!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-92",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[88/99] Jofash Resident: No, just right and chewy's what you want. Don't settle for anything more or less!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-93",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[89/99] Jofash Resident: Hmm, come to think. You seem really interested in discussin' bread with me!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-94",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[90/99] Jofash Resident: Lean in for a second, would you? I've got somethin' important to say.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-95",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[91/99] Jofash Resident: Listening? Right! Ah, sorry, I didn't mean to shout in your ear.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-96",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[92/99] Jofash Resident: You're just about the only person that I've been able to have an honest conversation about bread with.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-97",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[93/99] Jofash Resident: Usually, bread gets brushed off as some kind of dull fodder. Dismissed as too borin' and plain, I tell you! That's what leads to unnecessary excess as people try to make it into something that it's not.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-98",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[94/99] Jofash Resident: But us? We're different, we're visionaries, and we know the truth about what really makes a good loaf!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-99",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[95/99] Jofash Resident: Tell âem off, I say! They can't follow the thoughts of bread enthusiasts like you and I otherwise!",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-100",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[96/99] Jofash Resident: Ah! Right, I never did get to answerin' your question. About my favorite type of bread, that is...",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-101",
                false);
        s.addSound("[97/99] Jofash Resident: Plain ol' coarse-ground wheat.", "fantasticvoyage-breadman-102", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[98/99] Jofash Resident: Sure, it may be simple, but if you were payin' any attention at all, you'd know for sure why that's everythin' that I'm lookin' for.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-103",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[99/99] Jofash Resident: And that just about sums up the basics! Let me know if you want to hear anythin' more.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-104",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/564763] Bread Enthusiast: Let's continue! Have you ever seen a baker wearin' a fancy hat? Have you ever wondered how that corresponds to how well they bake bread compared to somethin' else?",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-105",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Jofash Resident: Aye!", "fantasticvoyage-breadman-106", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Jofash Resident: Hah! That crazy coot, you're chattin' with that feller?",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-107",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Jofash Resident: He's wack-o, y'know... Singing his songs all day, somethin's not right upstairs.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-108",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Jofash Resident: You do you, buddy, but I'd steer clear.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-109",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Jofash Resident: A parrot? You know where you are, right?",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-110",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Jofash Resident: I see plenty parrots everyday, I don't keep track.",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-111",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Jofash Resident: I'll keep an eye or two out for one, though, sound peachy?",
                "fantasticvoyage-breadman-112",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Jofash Clairvoyant: Welcome, welcome! How can I be of service to you, o' traveler?",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Jofash Clairvoyant: How can I be of service to you, o' traveler?",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Jofash Clairvoyant: Why, I am glad you asked, though I knew you would, of course!",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Jofash Clairvoyant: For you see... I am gifted with foresight, the futures memories come to me like no other!",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Jofash Clairvoyant: For the low, low price of [1 LE] , your future will be foretold!",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Jofash Clairvoyant: What do you say? Ha-ha, I ask out of courtesy, for I know what you will choose.",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Jofash Clairvoyant: Relend! Oh, the spirits have much to say of that man...",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Jofash Clairvoyant: More than most, he has seen... More than perhaps most should...",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Jofash Clairvoyant: Do not be fooled, o' traveler! Many a map has been snatched from his gnarled grasp...",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-9",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...perhaps your fortune shall reveal more! Worth a shot, hey?",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-10",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Jofash Clairvoyant: Aha... another one who follows the winged reaper...",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-11",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Jofash Clairvoyant: Yes... o' traveler... I have seen the parrot many a time... yes, indeed...",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-12",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Jofash Clairvoyant: Today, however, the wraith flies a unique way, one my eyes have not glimpsed.",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Jofash Clairvoyant: The keeper of the Tavern by my southern stall-mate will know its whereabouts...",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-14",
                false);
        s.addSound("[5/5] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...be wary, o' traveler.", "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-15", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: A wise choice, though expected, o' traveler!",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: Now... I must consult the spirits...",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-17",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...", "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-18", false);
        s.addSound("[4/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ......", "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-19", false);
        s.addSound("[5/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ..............", "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-20", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ..............................................",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-21",
                false);
        s.addSound("[7/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...", "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-22", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: Aha! O' traveler! Your fortune is as clear to me as the sky on a very clear day!",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-23",
                false);
        s.addSound("[9/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: You...", "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-24", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...will grow a little bit older, very soon!",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-25",
                false);
        s.addSound("[10/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...are being watched!", "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-26", false);
        s.addSound("[10/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...are really nice!", "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-27", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...will feel disappointed!",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-28",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...are going to lose [1 LE]!",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-29",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...should've watched your step!",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-30",
                false);
        s.addSound("[10/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...were homeless!", "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-31", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...are now breathing manually!",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-32",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...will find prosperity!", "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-33", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...enjoyed local cuisine!", "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-34", false);
        s.addSound("[10/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...really like bread!", "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-35", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/10] Jofash Clairvoyant: ...are going to get... a refund? What!? Oh, come on!",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-36",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Jofash Clairvoyant: Hello... hello! You have said... Hello!",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashclairvoyant-37",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Jofash Resident: Oh.. H-hello...", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-1", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Jofash Resident: C-Can I help you..?", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-2", false);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Jofash Resident: Uh? O-oh, yes, sorry...", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-3", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Jofash Resident: I'm doing j-just fine... Just.. I'm just fine...",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-4",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/4] Jofash Resident: I feel p-pretty good actually.", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-5", false);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Jofash Resident: Uh? I'm just... uh...", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-6", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Jofash Resident: I'm n-not sure... uh, actually...", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-7", false);
        s.addSound("[4/4] Jofash Resident: ...w-what are you doing?", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-8", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Jofash Resident: Uh? R-Relend..? Rel and w-who...?", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-9", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Jofash Resident: Uh.. I-I'm sorry, I don't know who you m-mean...",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-10",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/5] Jofash Resident: I'm, uh, well I'm, uh...", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-11", false);
        s.addSound("[5/5] Jofash Resident: ...sorry, I d-don't know...", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-12", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Jofash Resident: Ah... A-Alright...", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-13", false);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Jofash Resident: Uh? O-oh a parrot?", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-14", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Jofash Resident: L-L-Like a b-bird?! I l-love birds!",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-15",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/4] Jofash Resident: I will look for it... Human...", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-16", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Jofash Resident: Y-you can count o-on me... I will find the bird.",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-17",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Tavern Owner: Howdy, welcome to Jo's Tavern. What can I get for ya?",
                "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-1",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Tavern Owner: What can I get for ya?", "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-2", false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Tavern Owner: Oh, me? I'm doing just fine, mate.", "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-3", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Tavern Owner: This place is pretty popular among sailors, so we get a decent amount a' traffic for such a small place.",
                "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Tavern Owner: 's the only thing keeping me here, quite honestly. Lots'a crazies in this little town, it's nice to meet some normal folk, ya know?",
                "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-5",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Tavern Owner: One Nemract Whiskey, comin' up!", "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-6", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Tavern Owner: One Jofash Rum, comin' up!", "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-7", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Tavern Owner: One Llevigar Pinot, comin' up!", "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-8", false);
        s.addSound("[1/2] Tavern Owner: One Ahmsord Absinthe, comin' up!", "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-9", false);
        s.addSound("[2/2] Tavern Owner: ...you sure you like this stuff?", "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-10", false);
        s.addSound("[1/6] Tavern Owner: ...Relend? That old guy out front?", "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-11", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Tavern Owner: Typical resident here, if you ask me, totally nuts.",
                "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-12",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Tavern Owner: 's a weird one for sure, always speakin' in his little rhymes. Somethin's really snapped up there.",
                "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Tavern Owner: I've had loads a' folk come in here real angry 'bout the guy.",
                "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-14",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Tavern Owner: 'pparently he takes 'em for joyrides 'round the sea and get's all sorts'a labour out of 'em, then just drops 'em back here.",
                "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-15",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Tavern Owner: Ha! Guess he knows how to get some free work done, I'll give 'im that. Maybe he ain't so insane after all, eh?",
                "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Tavern Owner: ...Oh, you're goin' out with Relend, hey? Even after all I said?",
                "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-17",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Tavern Owner: Heh, have fun, mate. Lot'sa treasure out there, eh?",
                "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-18",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Tavern Owner: Well, whatever, mate. Yeah, the parrot's out on the patio, to the right of me, last I checked.",
                "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-19",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Tavern Owner: Have a nice trip, mate, if ya can catch it, that is. Heh...",
                "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-20",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Tavern Owner: No worries, let me know if you need anythin'",
                "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-21",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Tavern Owner: ...Didn't you hear me, mate? It's out on the tavern patio, to the right of me. The drinks not got t' ya already, has it?",
                "fantasticvoyage-tavernowner-22",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Jofash Resident: H-H-HUMAN!!!", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-18", false);
        s.addSound("[2/4] Jofash Resident: I-I-I SAW IT!!! THE B-BIRD!!!", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-19", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Jofash Resident: IT'S IN T-THE TREE, HERE! IT'S HERE!!!",
                "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-20",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/4] Jofash Resident: I f-found it... The bird...", "fantasticvoyage-jofashresident-21", false);
        s.addSound("[1/2] Relend: You have the map! Thank you for the assistance!", "fantasticvoyage-relend-10", false);
        s.addSound("[2/2] Relend: Now let us set sail, and cover some distance!", "fantasticvoyage-relend-11", false);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Relend: I'm sorry, new friend, to be of haste!", "fantasticvoyage-relend-12", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Relend: However I sense power in you, and we have no time to waste!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Relend: So off we go, to find an old friend, that would be ideal.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-14",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/4] Relend: I'll captain the ship up at the steering wheel.", "fantasticvoyage-relend-15", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Relend: Welcome aboard, I suppose I can consider you my first mate. Although, it appears we now have a problem on our plate.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Relend: You see those spikes all around my boat? Well, we're about to ram into them like a goat!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-17",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Relend: I'd steer around them, but it appears the wheel is all smashed. I need you to craft a new one before we both get splashed!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-18",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Relend: There's a Crafting Table at the front near all the crates. Now hurry up, else the ocean floor awaits!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-19",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Relend: There's a Crafting Table at the front near all the crates. Now hurry up, else the ocean floor awaits!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-20",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Relend: Ah, thank you for helping me in my time of need. Let's maneuver through these spikes at a steady speed!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-21",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Relend: Although, at the last minute, there is something I have to confess. I have never captained a ship with any success.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-22",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Relend: I think before we get into any real danger, we should turn around. Could you man the wheel and get us back to solid ground?",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-23",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Relend: I think before we get into any real danger, we should turn around. Could you man the wheel and get us back to solid ground?",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-24",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Relend: Now you're the captain, hope the sea's not making you nauseous. Steer this ship, but you'll have to be cautious!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-25",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Relend: Nice steering, although your maneuvers are a bit brash. Hey, watch out! I think we're about to-",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-26",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Relend: Trying to play captain, eh? Can't say I blame you. After all, who wouldn't want to sail the ocean blue?",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-27",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Relend: As you can see, my ship has become a shipwreck! Now please help me, I am trapped in the lower deck!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-28",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Relend: Amazing work, seems you got below deck rather quickly! You're going to have to get through this wreckage to free me!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-29",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Relend: Wow, so you managed to work your way through after all! Maybe to free me, you can use that cannonball?",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-30",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Relend: Thank you for freeing me, now let's leave this mess! Although, I don't know how  to do that, I have not even a guess.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-31",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Relend: When the ship crashed, it was buried beneath the sand! But the good news is that we're finally back on land!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-32",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Relend: We should probably get out of this place, it feels rather small. Perhaps you can try to break through that weak spot in the wall?",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-33",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Relend: We should probably get out of this place, it feels rather small. Perhaps you can try to break through that weak spot in the wall?",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-34",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Relend: It looks like we're going to be stuck here for a while. Come and speak to me so we can find a way off of this isle!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-35",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/7] Relend: Gateway Island... we've finally arri ved. I'm just thankful that we survived.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-36",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/7] Relend: Well, all this adventuring has me hungry for stew. We'll need ingredients, whatever's on the island will have to do.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-37",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/7] Relend: Meat is definitely something we need to reap, try and get [10 Raw Mutton] from those sheep.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-38",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/7] Relend: And perhaps you could get [5 Edible Mushrooms] from the western cave, just make sure not to get the kind that will send me to my grave.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-39",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/7] Relend: I feel like something is missing from this medley. Oh, how about you get [1 Coconut] from atop that tree?",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-40",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/7] Relend: And if you could fetch [7 Berries], that would just make me merry!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-41",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/7] Relend: Check your quest book if you ever need a recap. And to make sure you don't get lost, take the map.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-42",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Relend: Take a look at your quest book if you forgot your project, this island has supplies we ought to collect!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-43",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Relend: If you need to create something, there are utilities on the beach. I know that my old friend is someone we shall finally reach.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-44",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Relend: Well, this stew has a rather odd flavour. But any food we can get here I shall savour.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-45",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Relend: What remains of my ship won't protect us very well. We'll need to find shelter, as you can clearly tell.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-46",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Relend: To the east, I can just barely make out a tent. Go and look for my friend there, I'm simply hellbent!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-47",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/8] Relend: So the tent was all empty and run-down? All of this bad news is making me frown.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-48",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/8] Relend: Allow me to borrow your map for a second. We'll have to find him somewhere else, I reckon.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-49",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/8] Relend: I know we can come up with a solution using our wits. Perhaps we can craft an explosive to blow that big rock to bits!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-50",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/8] Relend: Let's think of some materials we can get here. There isn't much on this island, I fear.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-51",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/8] Relend: First we're going to need [5 Gritty Sand]. Where to get it? Try the beach at the back of the island.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-52",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/8] Relend: Next up is [Sawdust], you'll need three. I think the best place to search would be the largest tree.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-53",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/8] Relend: Finally, [1 Black Powder], found in a place that is very unique. You'll have to brave your way to the volcano's peak.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-54",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/8] Relend: You'll need those items to craft the bomb, I just told you where to look. If you forget what you need to find, check your content book.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-55",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Relend: Incredible, the explosive blew right through the stone!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-56",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/2] Relend: Let us progress into this mysterious zone.", "fantasticvoyage-relend-57", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/8] Relend: For adventurers like us, an incredible cave, perfect to explore.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-58",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/8] Relend: Surely where my old friend ventured - just as I swore!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-59",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/8] Relend: Long ago, a strong adventurer like yourself reached out to me for a wonderful sail. It truly is a gripping tale!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-60",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/8] Relend: We became the best of friends on our quest. But then he vanished, oh how he was the best.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-61",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/8] Relend: And we've finally made it to where he'd been. I can't wait to see him again, I don't know where to begin!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-62",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/8] Relend: A mystical portal! This must be where my old friend got lost!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-63",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/8] Relend: We must go through and find him, whatever the cost.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-64",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/2] Relend: I can't believe it! I simply can't speak!", "fantasticvoyage-relend-65", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Relend: I always told the others I wasn't a freak. Old friend, I'll look for you until the bitter end!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-66",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Relend: A foreign land filled with danger, to the brim...", "fantasticvoyage-relend-67", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Relend: It must be where he vanished to, regardless of how grim.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-68",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/6] Relend: My friend... Where do you think we are?", "fantasticvoyage-relend-69", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Relend: Wherever it is, I feel that we're being overseen from afar.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-70",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Relend: With all this danger, I do hope my good friend is still okay.",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-71",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Relend: My goodness! Keep your wits about, we may be in for a fray!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-72",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Relend: Aagh... new friend.. are you there?", "fantasticvoyage-relend-73", false);
        s.addSound("[2/4] Relend: Don't...give up... we must find him, I swear...", "fantasticvoyage-relend-74", false);
        s.addSound("[1/2] ???: â¤ââ­â­âââ£â¯ â â¤â§â  â¨'â°ââ¤â­â ââÃ³â¤â­ â â¤â¨â¢â£âââ£Ã¡â¤â§.", "fantasticvoyage-theeye-1", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Relend: I promise I'll find him, I'll do it, without a single scar!",
                "fantasticvoyage-relend-75",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/4] Relend: AAARRGHHHHH!", "fantasticvoyage-relend-76", false);
        s.addSound("[2/2] ???: â¤â¨â¤â¯â£â  ââ® â¨âª â­âââ£ââ­â, â¤ââ¤â­â¢â£âââ£Ã¡â§âÃ­.", "fantasticvoyage-theeye-2", false);

        // The feathers fly part 1
        s.addSound("[1/7] ???: Oh?! Hold on, is anyone there..!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-1", true);
        s.addSound("[2/7] Ava: Why hello there! Whatcha doin' here? I'm Ava!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-2", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/7] Ava: Want a quick job? How 'bout helpin' me out?! That was perfect timing!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/7] Ava: Y'see, while the other Avos hate it, I just find electromagic so fascinating!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/7] Ava: Look, I think I got a breakthrough invention. If it works... Oh man...",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/7] Ava: I just need to harness some nature magic, and there's an amazing source in the chief's hut. Ya comin'?",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/7] Ava: Don't you worry about rewards! I got you! See ya' there!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-7",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/6] Ava: Hey! You showed up! Listen up, here's the plan...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-8", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Ava: There's a small museum inside the hut with all kinds of trophies.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-9",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Ava: Our chief is quite the talkative fella, and I can guarantee he'd love to tell you stories.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-10",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Ava: That should keep him and his guards busy. And that's where I come in!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-11",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Ava: I'll take that chance to sneak behind the throne, where our sacred totem is. I'm not stealing it, don't worry!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-12",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Ava: I'm a little clumsy, but I'm sure I can count on ya'! No matter what, keep the chief busy!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Avos Chieftain: Greetings, human. Welcome back.", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-1", false);
        s.addSound("[2/5] Avos Chieftain: So, what brings you here, hm?", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-2", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Avos Chieftain: Oh, you want to learn more about us... Of course, of course!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Avos Chieftain: We have a room where I can show you some of our history.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Avos Chieftain: You're in luck, I'm in a good mood. Follow me then.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-5",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/2] Avos Chief: Ah, history first! Great, great!", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschief-1", false);
        s.addSound("[1/2] Avos Chief: Gah! You startled me!", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschief-2", false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Avos Chief: Ah, our wisteria tree! Yes...", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschief-3", false);
        s.addSound("[1/2] Avos Chief: Oh, this is quite the important tome.", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschief-4", false);
        s.addSound("[1/2] Avos Chief: Right, the feathery crate!", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschief-5", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Avos Chieftain: What was that?! I'll check.", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-6", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Avos Chieftain: Someone broke in? But why? Anyone can use our totem...",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Avos Chieftain: I don't get it. They could've just asked...",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-8",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/7] Ava: Oh, hey! Thanks for earlier. You were a big help.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-14", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/7] Ava: Truth is, anyone can use that totem. They just don't like me very much.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-15",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/7] Ava: Anyway, we got what we needed, and it's promising! Now onto the next part...",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/7] Ava: Y'see, I managed to bottle up some of our magic, but I still need Corkian stuff.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-17",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/7] Ava: Fortunately for us, there's a shop outside the city. Though, things might get complicated...",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-18",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/7] Ava: A bunch of Corkians aren't too fond of... Us. I just think you should come along with me, y'know?",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-19",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/7] Ava: Here, I wrote the coords into that book of yours. It's a bit far, so come on out and I'll give you a lift!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-20",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Ava: Alright, if you want a lift, tell me, or you could just walk!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-21",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Ava: Not sure why you'd do that when I'm right here though!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-22",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Alright, buckle up, we're taking off!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-23", true);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Still holding on? We're almost there!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-24", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Ava: Here we are! Enjoyed the lift? I'm a great form of fast travel, right?!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-25",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Ava: Well, this was my first time using this magic magnet on people, but...",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-26",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ava: Or I guess you could just leave, that's cool too...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-27", false);
        s.addSound("[1/6] Ava: Ah, finally! I could've taken you there y'know!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-28", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Ava: Honestly, I just wanted to test something on you... Oh well!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-29",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Ava: This is the shop! I think we can buy an Enhanced Potential Microchip here. ",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-30",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/6] Ava: I need you to accompany me.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-31", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Ava: If I'm with a human, surely they'll sell one, right?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-32", false);
        s.addSound("[6/6] Ava: You go first, I'll follow you.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-33", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Shopkeeper: Hmpf. What are you doing in here, Avo?!", "thefeathersflypart1-shopkeeper-1", false);
        s.addSound("[2/6] Ava: So-uh, I was, y'know, wonderin' if you had any-", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-34", false);
        s.addSound("[3/6] Shopkeeper: Huh?!", "thefeathersflypart1-shopkeeper-2", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Shopkeeper: There's NO WAY I'm selling anythin' to an Avo! Shoo! Get out!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-shopkeeper-3",
                false);
        s.addSound("[5/6] Ava: But...! ", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-35", false);
        s.addSound("[6/6] Shopkeeper: OUT!", "thefeathersflypart1-shopkeeper-4", true);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Ava: I... can't believe this.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-36", false);
        s.addSound("[2/4] Ava: I am NOT giving up! To hell with all this!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-37", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Ava: Here, go in yourself and ask. I'll cover the cost later.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-38",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Ava: I'll stand back. CLEARLY this guy is too STUCK up to- Ugh, I'm getting angry! Just go in again.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-39",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Shopkeeper: Huh?! I made myself clear! You were with her!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-shopkeeper-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Shopkeeper: I'm closing for today, I cannot stand this! OUT!!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-shopkeeper-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Shopkeeper: Oh, and don't even think about even approaching MY shop!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-shopkeeper-7",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Hang tight! He's gone crazy!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-40", true);
        s.addSound("[1/7] Ava: Urgh, this guy's nuts. Hmm...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-41", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/7] Ava: I'm... surprised he kicked you out, too. Maybe he's a patriot?",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-42",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/7] Ava: Well, anyway, we need a plan. I don't wanna wait this out.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-43",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/7] Ava: Look, this guy has to have a control panel somewhere. Maybe we can neutralize the robots.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-44",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/7] Ava: That stuff hates water, y'know? So I'll go fetch some in the meantime.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-45",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/7] Ava: I'd like to NOT get zapped by a forcefield, so I'll sneak inside once we're done with that.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-46",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/7] Ava: Got it? Find the control panel. It should be somewhere around the house. Talk to me once you're ready.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-47",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ava: Good luck, then! I'll be back once you find the control panel and get inside!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-48",
                true);
        s.addSound("[1/5] Ava: Here we are! Good job! Alright, let's see...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-49", false);
        s.addSound("[2/5] Ava: Wait... Why are there... Buttons... Everywhere??", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-50", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Ava: I feel like soaking everything would be quite the mistake.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-51",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/5] Ava: And none of them are labelled! What is that?!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-52", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Ava: Look, your choice. What should we neutralize first?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-53", false);
        s.addSound("[1/2] Ava: Left, huh? Well, let's see how that goes.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-54", false);
        s.addSound("[2/2] Ava: Alright, let's soak this.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-55", false);
        s.addSound("!safetyteleportationsequenceactivated!", "thefeathersflypart1-security-1", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: TELEPORTATION?!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-56", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Ava: Center... I guess the most important stuff could be here. In theory. I wouldn't count on it.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-57",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Ava: Huh! This wasn't that bad. And... I see something poking out, hold on...",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-58",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/5] Ava: Haha! I think that's what we're looking for!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-59", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Ava: Look, I still want to make it up to the guy. I really don't want to be the villain of his story.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-60",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Ava: I'll meet you back at the Workshop. You can go on ahead.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-61",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Ava: Right, right. Stand back, just in case.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-62", false);
        s.addSound("[!] ERROR! Defense protocols shutdown...", "thefeathersflypart1-security-2", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Ava: Oh wow. You got the right one, first try! How'd you know?",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-63",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Ava: Well, good job. I still want to make it up to the poor guy though.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-64",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/4] Ava: Just meet me back at the Workshop, I'll be there!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-65", false);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Ava: Ouch!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-66", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Ava: Sorry about all the trouble I caused... I hope this makes it up to you.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-67",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Ava: I hope that human's alright... I managed to find the microchip right away, after all.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-68",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Ava: ...Alright. Time to go. I'll wait for them, I guess.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-69", false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Ava: Ouch!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-70", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Ava: Sorry about all the trouble I caused... I hope this makes it up to you.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-71",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/3] Ava: ...Alright. Time to go.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-72", false);
        s.addSound("[1/2] Ava: Oh, there you are! I felt sad leaving you behind!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-73", false);
        s.addSound("[2/2] Ava: Say, if you need a lift, just tell me.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-74", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Alright then, buckle up!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-75", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Alright, I'm dropping you off! Stick the landing!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-76", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/7] Ava: I can't believe it! It's working! Look! Look at it!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-77", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/7] Ava: A Growth Accelerator... Can you imagine the possibilities?!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-78",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/7] Ava: We'll be able to... I don't know, help the poor, that's nice, right?",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-79",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/7] Ava: But we're not done. Well, I'm not done. I'd still like your help.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-80",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/7] Ava: Look, let's try it out together, alright? Maybe I'll let you go afterwards?",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-81",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/7] Ava: I'll join you outside. Once I'm sure this works, I'll be able to... Show it to them.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-82",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/7] Ava: In theory, it should be easy to operate... I'm trusting you. Again. Sorry 'bout that.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-83",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Ava: Alright, it's just on the hill next to us, but I can bring you there if ya want!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-84",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Ava: Just don't get too used to me, alright? Tell me when you're ready.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-85",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Here we go!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-86", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Ava: I'll do a quick rundown of how to operate this. It's not automatic yet.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-87",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Ava: I'll give you a remote. You'll simply have to click in the right orders. You'll see!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-88",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Ava: You have to be quick, though! You can't just take all the time you want.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-89",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Ava: I have no clue how stable all of this is, so we'll start slowly!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-90",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Ava: I know this sounds a li'l scary, but you've shown yourself being capable.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-91",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Ava: Tell me when you're ready, I'll give you the remote then start the machine!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-92",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Ava: Ready? Take this first.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-93", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Ava: Think of it like... Casting one of your spells. You're used to that, right?",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-94",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Ava: Let's start slowly! You have 45 seconds to fully charge it up!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-95",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Halfway there!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-96", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: And now, we observe!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-97", false);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Ava: Oh my... I- No way...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-98", false);
        s.addSound("[2/4] Ava: Do you have ANY idea what it is we've just done?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-99", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Ava: I have to show that to the Chief. They WILL accept me! I cannot fail now!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-100",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Ava: Tell you what, let's meet up at the Chief's hut. If you want me to take you there right now, you can just go ahead and tell me!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-101",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/6] Ava: Alright, let's fly!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-102", true);
        s.addSound("[2/6] Ava: It really is convenient being with me, huh?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-103", true);
        s.addSound("[3/6] Ava: On second thought... Isn't it too soon?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-104", true);
        s.addSound("[4/6] Ava: I-I think I want to turn back... I...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-105", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Ava: Gah! If I can't get myself to do it now, I'll never do it!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-106",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Ava: You should approach the Chief first. It... won't work if I do it. I'll come by afterwards.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-107",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/12] Avos Chieftain: Ah, human! Welcome back. Good timing...",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-9",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/12] Avos Chieftain: Did you happen to see... An oddly dressed Avo around here recently?",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-10",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/12] Avos Chieftain: We kicked that girl from the tribe, and we do have our reasons.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-11",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/12] Avos Chieftain: I've heard reports of her snooping around recently. With a human, even.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-12",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/12] Avos Chieftain: And I believe... That this is no coincidence you're here.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/12] Avos Chieftain: I will be frank. You're with her, aren't you? I won't hurt you. I won't hurt her either.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-14",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/12] Avos Chieftain: She's not exactly welcome here. But she's never told you about that, did she?",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-15",
                false);
        s.addSound("[8/12] Ava: And I have nothing to hide, Chief.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-108", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[9/12] Avos Chieftain: STOP IT, you two! Let her talk!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/12] Ava: You're all scared of change, and that's all there is to it. Now...",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-109",
                false);
        s.addSound("[11/12] Ava: May I... Show you something?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-110", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[12/12] Avos Chieftain: Hmpf. Let's see that broken atrocity of yours.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-17",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: ...It's time. Talk to me.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-111", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Ava: This is it. I can't fail now... I really hope I can trust you.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-112",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/4] Ava: You have no idea how important this is to me.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-113", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Ava: It'll be slightly more difficult than last time, so get ready.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-114",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/4] Ava: I'll give you the remote once you're ready!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-115", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Avos Chieftain: I truly hope this will work, for once.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-18",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Avos Chieftain: Wait, are you sure this isn't dang-",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-19",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/2] Ava: Don't worry 'bout that!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-116", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Let's do this!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-117", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Here we go!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-118", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Oh god, no- Let me boot up the machine again...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-119", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Alright... Talk to me.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-120", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Ava: Let's just say... Failure is part of the process?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-121", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Ava: I-You-no, I can't blame anyone. Let's just do this again.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-122",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Avos Chieftain: Hm. I was almost hopeful this time.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-20",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/3] Ava: T-talk to me once you're ready to try again.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-123", false);
        s.addSound("[2/3] Ava: C-Chief, we... we got this, don't worry!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-124", false);
        s.addSound("[3/3] Ava: 't would've been too good to be false, right?", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-125", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Avos Chieftain: ...Was anything supposed to happen?",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-21",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/3] Ava: Just... Get ready.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-126", false);
        s.addSound("[1/2] Avos Guard: That's it, I-", "thefeathersflypart1-avosguard-1", false);
        s.addSound("[2/2] Avos Chief: Let's just give her a chance for now.", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschief-6", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Avos Chieftain: Hmm... Interesting...", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-22", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Avos Guard: Why is she getting away with using such magic?!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avosguard-2",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Avos Guard: Tch. How horrible...", "thefeathersflypart1-avosguard-3", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Oh I'm gonna charge this sapling like crazy!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-127", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Alright, this is the last stretch!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-128", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ava: One last time soldier, and I'm counting on you to be quick!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-129",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Stand back... Almost there! ", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-130", false);
        s.addSound("[1/8] Avos Chieftain: ...Oh my!", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-23", false);
        s.addSound("[2/8] Ava: Wait... That's it?? No, this isn't right...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-131", false);
        s.addSound("[3/8] Ava: Let me just...", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-132", false);
        s.addSound("[4/8] Avos Chieftain: WAIT!", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-24", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/8] Avos Guard: Chief! Have you seen what she just did?!", "thefeathersflypart1-avosguard-4", false);
        s.addSound("[6/8] Ava: I-I didn't mean to! I told you to stand back!!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-133", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/8] Avos Chieftain: Under normal circumstances, I'd have sent you down the pit after cutting off your feathers.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-25",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/8] Avos Chieftain: But these are not normal circumstances. Soldier, may you come over here as well?",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-26",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/10] Avos Chieftain: So you fused OUR magic... With electromagic?",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-27",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/10] Avos Chieftain: I recognized extracts from the totem too. You're the one who stole from us, right?",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-28",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/10] Ava: I... might have done that.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-134", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/10] Avos Chieftain: And on top of that, you used the Wynn warrior to fool us?",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-29",
                false);
        s.addSound("[5/10] Ava: And I'm sure you know why I did!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-135", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/10] Avos Chieftain: Do you have any idea how unstable this wretched electromagic is?!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-30",
                false);
        s.addSound("[7/10] Ava: I-I can control it!!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-136", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/10] Avos Chieftain: And you should NOT! Don't you understand? This is too dangerous!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-31",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[9/10] Avos Guard: Should we kill her on the spot?! We almost died!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avosguard-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/10] Avos Chieftain: No, don't kill her. I want her and the soldier in my hut, now.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-32",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/11] Avos Chieftain: Ava. You can't keep going with this. Just stop. This is your final warning.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-33",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/11] Avos Chieftain: What do you even hope to accomplish? You used to be such a brilliant kid.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-34",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/11] Ava: I just... wanna help people. You know that, I'm sure you understand!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-137",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/11] Avos Chieftain: Have you seen the Factory? They tried to help people, and instead they killed hundreds!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-35",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/11] Avos Chieftain: Do you think you're able change the world?! Well, you can't, Ava! This is beyond you!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-36",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/11] Avos Chieftain: So, for the last time. Stop all of this. I might reconsider your banishment then.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-37",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/11] Ava: You... You're really serious about that, huh? You'll NEVER change, will you?!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-138",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/11] Ava: Do you guys have ANY idea how archaic you all are?! A ''final warning''??",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-139",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[9/11] Ava: To hell with this! I'll show everyone! I'll show how great we could be! You'll see, chief!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-140",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/11] Avos Chieftain: I can't believe you worked with her, soldier. Well, now you know to avoid her.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-38",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[11/11] Avos Chieftain: ...It appears she left some device on the floor. You might as well take them, I sure don't want it. And here, take these. We haven't had the chance to thank you regarding the Factory.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-39",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Hey, don't run  off just like that!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-141", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ava: Alright, this should be good. Talk to me and I'll explain!",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-142",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ava: Oh, you're back! Talk to me so we can get started!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-143", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ava: Oh no, time's up! It was supposed to be easy... Hold on, I'm booting it up again.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-144",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Ava: Hey, it happens to the best of us!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-145", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Ava: It's fine, the machine isn't at full power, it won't explode or anything.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-ava-146",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/3] Ava: Just tell me when you're ready!", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-147", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: I have faith in you", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-148", false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Ava: We'll, uh, act as if nothing happened.", "thefeathersflypart1-ava-149", false);
        s.addSound("[1/2] Avos Chief: Hey, would you listen to me?", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschief-7", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Avos Chieftain: Is that another broken machine?", "thefeathersflypart1-avoschieftain-40", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Avos Chieftain: Just show me what you're interested about.",
                "thefeathersflypart1-avoschief-8",
                false);

        // the feathers fly part 2
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Gardener: An audience? Oh, you're one of those, I see...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-gardener-1",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/5] Gardener: ...Huh? An audience? Are you crazy?", "thefeathersflypart2-gardener-2", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Weaponsmith: Oh, are you interested in getting an audience too?!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-weaponsmith-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Corkus Citizen: Oh, please don't mention the word \"audience\" to me!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-corkuscitizen-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Corkus Citizen: Why hello there you two! Whaddya want? An audience, huh? Eheh...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-corkuscitizen-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Corkus Citizen: Why thank you! 't was a pleasure doing business with you keheh... Good luck!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-corkuscitizen-3",
                true);
        s.addSound("[1/5] Receptionist: ...Wait, who are YOU?", "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-1", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] ???: OUT!", "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-2", false);
        s.addSound("[2/3] Corkus Citizen: You're the WORST!!", "thefeathersflypart2-corkuscitizen-4", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Receptionist: Wow. I cannot stop staring at you... Such magnificent armour.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Receptionist: Well, you two seem very lucky, there's an available slot soon!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Receptionist: And just WHO are you two busting here like that?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Receptionist: Do you have ANYTHING to show? Shouldn't you be working at that time?!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Receptionist: Not ANOTHER word! I've heard enough! You two clearly don't have anything worth my time!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Receptionist: Go back to your minimum wage job or something, but stay OUT of my room.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/8] Receptionist: Why hello there! Greetings! Welcome! You are looking splendid, dear! ",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-9",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/8] Receptionist: Don't be sillydear, you're beautiful! Say, you're looking to be an investor, am I right?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-10",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/8] Receptionist: Why of course! Is that other person your assistant? Great!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-11",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/8] Receptionist: I'd like you to show me you have what it takes to be a great investor, yes!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-12",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/8] Receptionist: Just hand over a mere 12 Liquified Emeralds and it's settled!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Receptionist: And just WHO are you two, busting here like that?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-14",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Receptionist: Do you have ANYTHING to show? I need more than fancy clothes.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-15",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Receptionist: And what's up with your face, lady? I'd look into that if I were you! OUT!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/8] Receptionist: Oh god, not another duo. What do you want?!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-17",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/8] Receptionist: And what would a mechanic have for- Wait, is that an invitation letter..?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-18",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/8] Receptionist: That's... Unprecedented. Let me check when the council's available and book an audience...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-19",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/8] Receptionist: You two are extremely lucky. I can barely believe it.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-20",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/8] Receptionist: I hope tomorrow morning is good for you, because the Council's somehow available at that time.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-21",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/8] Receptionist: Sounds good? Hopefully it does, because you don't really have much of a choice. Well, you can leave now.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-22",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/8] Receptionist: Oh! Why hello there you two! How may I be of assistance?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-23",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/8] Receptionist: You're looking splendid dear! Now, are you-- Wait, you have a letter?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-24",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/8] Receptionist: You know miss, you look like you could've been a great investor. Oh well, good luck!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-25",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/8] Receptionist: Why sure darling, you have 3 seconds to- Hold on, that letter...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-26",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/8] Receptionist: That's... Unprecedented. Let me check when the council's avaliable and book an audience... ",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-27",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/8] Receptionist: I hope tomorrow morning is good for you.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-28",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/8] Receptionist: Don't miss it. Oh, and miss, there's something really off about your face.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-29",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/8] Receptionist: If you want a tip, well... There's a new guy in the council, so he might be easier to impress!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-30",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Receptionist: Urgh, what now? You better be quick.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-receptionist-31",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/20] Grant: Hmpf. Is he late?", "thefeathersflypart2-grant-1", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/20] Mei: Nah, I saw him running around earlier. He's coming.", "thefeathersflypart2-mei-1", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/20] Efena: My guts are telling me this one's gonna be impressive. I hope he's there.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-1",
                false);
        s.addSound("[7/20] Clomius: Oh, I hear him.", "thefeathersflypart2-clomius-1", false);
        s.addSound("[8/20] Efena: Sharp ear.", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-2", false);
        s.addSound("[9/20] Clomius: Always.", "thefeathersflypart2-clomius-2", false);
        s.addSound("[10/20] Maxie: Sorry, sorry, I'm here! Am I late?!", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-1", false);
        s.addSound("[11/20] Nodise: We haven't started yet. You're fine.", "thefeathersflypart2-nodise-1", false);
        s.addSound("[12/20] Maxie: Phew, I tho- Wait, soldier??", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-2", false);
        s.addSound("[13/20] Sybil: You know them?! How?!", "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-1", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[13/20] Sybil: Of course you'd know them. I'm not surprised.", "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-17", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[13/20] Sybil: And lo and behold, you know them. Of course.", "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-19", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[14/20] Maxie: How do you not?! They're the one who helped deal with the Factory!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[15/20] Efena: ...So it's you. I somehow imagined you... More imposing. Huh.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-3",
                false);
        s.addSound("[17/20] Dwice: Shall we begin, pres'?", "thefeathersflypart2-dwice-1", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[18/20] Efena: Ava, was it? The handwriting's odd. Well, welcome to... the Council!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-4",
                false);
        s.addSound("[19/20] Efena: I'm Efena, President of Corkus!", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-5", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[20/20] Efena: *ahem*It's up to you, now. Do your thing. What do you have in store for us?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Carl: A mechanic? Which area? Maybe I have a friend wh-", "thefeathersflypart2-carl-1", false);
        s.addSound("[3/6] Grant: Shut it Carl, let her talk.", "thefeathersflypart2-grant-2", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/7] Sybil: Y'know, you really don't look like the \"inventor\" type.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-2",
                false);
        s.addSound("[5/7] Nodise: Plants, huh? That's unusual, I'm curious.", "thefeathersflypart2-nodise-2", false);
        s.addSound("[3/7] Efena: Huh! Go on...", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-7", false);
        s.addSound("[2/6] Mei: I see you're familiar with your toy!", "thefeathersflypart2-mei-2", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Sybil: Wait, you brought such an armour and that's not what you're showcasing?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-3",
                false);
        s.addSound("[5/6] Clomius: You certainly caught our attention. Go on.", "thefeathersflypart2-clomius-3", false);
        s.addSound("[2/3] Efena: And we sure hope so!", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-8", false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Grant: Hmpf. What's happening?", "thefeathersflypart2-grant-3", false);
        s.addSound("[2/3] Maxie: I think we should give them a bit more time.", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-4", false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Efena: Are you two sure you're alright?", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-9", false);
        s.addSound("[2/3] Efena: Is that machine that hard to control?", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-10", false);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Efena: Alright, you really seem to be struggling.", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-11", false);
        s.addSound("[2/4] Efena: Lucky for you, I'm in a relatively good mood.", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-12", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Efena: I'm giving you 6 more tries before we call it quits.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Efena: Hey, even I'm worried for you now. 5 tries left.", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-14", false);
        s.addSound("[2/3] Mei: You don't want to anger Efena.", "thefeathersflypart2-mei-3", false);
        s.addSound("[3/3] Grant: Hmpf. Show us your best this time.", "thefeathersflypart2-grant-4", false);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Efena: 4 tries left.", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-15", false);
        s.addSound("[2/4] Maxie: ...Aren't you stressing them out... Too much?", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-5", false);
        s.addSound("[3/4] Sybil: Don't spoil our fun, Maxie!", "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-4", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Efena: Your fun. I'm not a monster. It's called time management, Sybil.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Efena: 3 tries left. I hate to do this to you, but we have strict schedules.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-17",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/4] Dwice: Oh we can definitely see that.", "thefeathersflypart2-dwice-2", false);
        s.addSound("[4/4] Efena: Let's not make it worse for them.", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-18", false);
        s.addSound("[1/4] Efena: 2 tries left...", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-19", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Efena: Sorry. Maybe you should've showcased that armour instead.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-20",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Efena: By all means, continue. Ninth time's the charm.", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-21", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Efena: Last chance, Ava. This was quite the audience, but we're very much used to that.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-22",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Efena: Actually, how'd you get one in the first place? Just curious. ",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-23",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Efena: Cryptic. I'd have liked that more if you and soldier knew what you were doing.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-24",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/6] Nodise: What a shame. I believed in these two.", "thefeathersflypart2-nodise-3", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Clomius: So did I. But you heard Efena. I guess it's over.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-clomius-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Efena: Fine. I'll give you one pass. You do have a cool armour, after all.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-25",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Clomius: Fancy.", "thefeathersflypart2-clomius-5", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Efena: Even I'm getting into this!", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-26", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Efena: ...Huh.", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-27", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Nodise: I do believe this has potential. Let us see more of it.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-nodise-4",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Efena: I like the sounds, at least!", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-28", false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Dwice: This almost reminds me of, uuuh...", "thefeathersflypart2-dwice-3", false);
        s.addSound("[2/3] Dwice: Hold on, it's on the tip of my tongue...", "thefeathersflypart2-dwice-4", false);
        s.addSound("[3/3] Dwice: Ah right, Avos magic! Right??", "thefeathersflypart2-dwice-5", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Efena: So soldier knows how to handle machines too? Nifty!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-29",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/6] Maxie: Wait, don't overdo it!", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-6", false);
        s.addSound("[6/6] Maxie: Wait, that magic, that's... No...", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-7", false);
        s.addSound("[1/10] Efena: Oh my... Oh my grook. This is... Wow...", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-30", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/10] Efena: It's the real deal. That girl managed to instantly overgrow a flower.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-31",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/10] Mei: ...Don't look at us like that, I'm as surprised as you are.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-mei-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/10] Efena: Well, Ava... You've won me over. I'm impressed!  ",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-32",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/10] Efena: Hey, you alright? Itâs not often mechanics impress us. Good job.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-33",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/10] Efena: Youâre crying?! Aw... There, there. Itâs alright, you made it.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-34",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/10] Efena: I didn't really doubt you with your armour. We have a few questions though!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-35",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/10] Carl: This is all really nice, but... How does this work?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-carl-2",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Carl: Oh, that component, that's a-.", "thefeathersflypart2-carl-3", false);
        s.addSound("[7/10] Efena: Shut it, Carl! No one c- Wait. Actually...", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-36", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/10] Efena: No one in Corkus ever made anything like this. Do you have anything to tell us, or show?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-37",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[9/10] Efena: While the machine didn't seem to work, you pulled out some... Weird magic. Are you hiding anything?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-38",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/15] Everyone: WHAT?", "thefeathersflypart2-everyone-1", false);
        s.addSound("[3/15] Sybil: There's NO WAY that's true!", "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-5", false);
        s.addSound("[4/15] Mei: What should we do what should we-", "thefeathersflypart2-mei-5", false);
        s.addSound("[5/15] Dwice: Should we seize her?!", "thefeathersflypart2-dwice-6", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Dwice: Flawless?! More like flawful! This was so obvious!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-dwice-7",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/6] Dwice: I- uh, y'know, didn't want to assume...", "thefeathersflypart2-dwice-8", false);
        s.addSound("[7/15] Mei: I don't- I don't know!", "thefeathersflypart2-mei-6", false);
        s.addSound("[9/15] Sybil: You SHUT UP for now!", "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-6", false);
        s.addSound("[10/15] Maxie: Maybe she-", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-8", false);
        s.addSound("[11/15] Sybil: 'goes for you too, Maxie!", "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-7", false);
        s.addSound("[12/15] Nodise: Let's calm down and start ag-", "thefeathersflypart2-nodise-5", false);
        s.addSound("[13/15] Clomius: So that explains the magic!", "thefeathersflypart2-clomius-6", false);
        s.addSound("[13/15] Clomius: I just can't believe this!!", "thefeathersflypart2-clomius-7", false);
        s.addSound("[14/15] Grant: Hmpf? Just take her on the spot!", "thefeathersflypart2-grant-5", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[15/15] Efena: EVERYONE! STOP! Soldier, I want you to come here and answer something, immediately.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-39",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Efena: We wouldn't have known with such an outfit.", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-40", false);
        s.addSound("[2/3] Efena: There's only one thing I want to know.", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-41", false);
        s.addSound("[3/3] Efena: Did you know, or did she trick you?", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-42", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/20] Efena: Sure, and then what? What did you hope to accomplish?!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-43",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/20] Efena: I'm unsure if I should be impressed, distressed or enraged. So I think I'll just be all three. Ava, congratulations.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-44",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/20] Efena: Oh, darling. You impress then enrage me, and now you want me to pity you.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-45",
                false);
        s.addSound("[7/20] Efena: You know, your kind has always been...", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-46", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/20] Efena: So archaic. Always with their spirituality, their flora, their beliefs, their traditions...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-47",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/20] Efena: I thought electromagic was limited to humans, but it seems like you're miserable at it anyway.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-48",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[11/20] Efena: Even then, I see no reason as to why we should let you interact with us. You shouldn't be here.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-49",
                false);
        s.addSound("[17/20] Sybil: Alright, I've heard enough. That's it.", "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-8", false);
        s.addSound("[18/20] Nodise: Sybil, wait!", "thefeathersflypart2-nodise-6", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[20/20] Efena: What just... Everyone! Dismissed! What is that girl doing?! I'll go after her! Nodise, Maxie, you go and help Sybil!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-50",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/8] Maxie: Well... Mo'in, soldier. I was thinking about catching up with you and all after the audience, but...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-9",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/8] Maxie: I guess we don't really have time for that now, do we?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-10",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/8] Sybil: Wow, Maxie, great time management you got there!", "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-9", false);
        s.addSound("[4/8] Nodise: Sybil... This is no time to quarrel.", "thefeathersflypart2-nodise-7", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/8] Sybil: Have you seen what just happened? I'm sure even now he'll keep defending the Avos!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-10",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/8] Maxie: Look, there's no time right now. I think soldier and I should go and help.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-11",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/8] Maxie: Nodise... You probably should stay here too. We-", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-12", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/8] Maxie: Wha-What's happening?! Oh dear, I'll just run there!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/8] Sybil: You're- *cough*so good at handling... priorities, Maxie.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-11",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/8] Nodise: Save your energy for later, Sybil.", "thefeathersflypart2-nodise-8", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/8] Sybil: Even after... Even after this, I'm sure *cough*he'll keep defending them...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-12",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Efena: Well look who decided to show up. I thought you would've fled by now.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-51",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Maxie: Soldier!! I'm sure Efena told you already, no time to talk!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-14",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Maxie: Apparently, there's something up there! Try to reach the top! There are strange plants around, see if that helps!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-15",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Maxie: No time to talk! Just go! There must be a core to hit at the top!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Maxie: Woah! You did something! You should try that again!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-17",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Grant: Hmpf! Leave me be! If you want to climb to reason with your friend, hit some of these weird plants, they seem to throw people around! You don't even need a weapon.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-grant-6",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/6] Efena: Soldier! Ava's up there, isn't she?", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-52", false);
        s.addSound("[1/10] Mei: ...Everyone alright?", "thefeathersflypart2-mei-7", false);
        s.addSound("[2/10] Grant: Hmpf. Did soldier take that thing down?", "thefeathersflypart2-grant-7", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Grant: Hmpf. I certainly am curious now.", "thefeathersflypart2-grant-8", false);
        s.addSound("[3/10] Mei: 'think so, yeah.", "thefeathersflypart2-mei-8", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Mei: Interesting.", "thefeathersflypart2-mei-9", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Mei: Urgh, what is this thing made of..! Should I go higher?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-mei-10",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/10] Maxie: Where's soldier? And Ava?!", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-18", false);
        s.addSound("[5/10] Efena: Oh she better be around here!", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-53", false);
        s.addSound("[6/10] Maxie: Wait, under the rubble, I see something!", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-19", false);
        s.addSound("[7/10] Maxie: There! Soldier, are you alright? Hello?", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-20", false);
        s.addSound("[8/10] Efena: They unconscious?", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-54", false);
        s.addSound("[9/10] Maxie: It... It looks like it.", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-21", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/10] Efena: Look, I'll give you a mission. Find Ava with soldier, and tell her this...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-55",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Maxie: Soldier?! 'that you? I'm downstairs!", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-22", true);
        s.addSound("[1/8] Maxie: Mo'in, soldier! You're fine! I'm so glad!", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-23", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Maxie: Alright, let's get going.", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-24", false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Maxie: ...There? *sigh*I hope she's inside.", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-25", false);
        s.addSound("[1/9] Maxie: ...Huh.", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-26", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/9] Maxie: The Avos chief did mention her once, but this place is crazy!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-27",
                false);
        s.addSound("[5/9] Maxie: Ava... I-", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-28", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/9] Maxie: The president didn't sentence you to death or anything... Quite the opposite, actually.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-29",
                false);
        s.addSound("[9/9] Maxie: Well, it's just that-", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-30", false);
        s.addSound("[1/27] ???: Don't bother, Maxie. I'll explain myself.", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-56", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/27] Efena: Nice place. I can clearly see how our culture got to you.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-57",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/27] Efena: Oh, \"forgive\" is a really strong word, Ava. Look.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-58",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/27] Efena: I do believe we can all learn a thing or two about this. Ava...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-59",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/27] Efena: You broke the law, and as such, you're not allowed in town. Ya understand?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-60",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/27] Efena: Look, that machine of yours is impressive. I'm not lying. You're talented.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-61",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[9/27] Efena: But you've definitely made quite the mistake. I did too.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-62",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/27] Efena: I guess you and I really learnt what ''acting in the heat of the moment'' means, huh.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-63",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[11/27] Efena: I have some sort of... Compromise. For us. Maxie?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-64",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[12/27] Maxie: Yeah, I'm... interested in working with you. Learning from you.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-31",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[13/27] Maxie: You're clearly better at Electromagic than I, so...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-32",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[14/27] Maxie: I'm willing to provide you with what you need. Help you out from time to time.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-33",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[15/27] Efena: You've been alone for so long, Ava. I'm lending you Maxie!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-65",
                false);
        s.addSound("[16/27] Maxie: Hey, don't say it like that!", "thefeathersflypart2-maxie-34", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[17/27] Efena: *chuckles*I'm kidding. The rest of the council isn't aware yet.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-66",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[18/27] Efena: They're not gonna like this, but I'll handle it.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-67",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[19/27] Efena: You know I can't kill you. Can you imagine how the Avos would take it? Even though you're banished...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-68",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[20/27] Efena: But I don't want to either. As for you, soldier...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-69",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[21/27] Efena: I'll give you some stuff. I can't imagine how things would've gone if it weren't for you.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-70",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[22/27] Efena: Now, you're banished from everyone Ava. I know that's no happy ending.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-71",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[23/27] Efena: But that would've been too easy, don't ya think?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-72",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[24/27] Efena: Maybe later, you'll get your happy ending. But you can settle with not being alone anymore, right?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-73",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[25/27] Efena: Goodbye, Ava. Who knows, maybe I'll stop by sometimes.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-74",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[25/27] Efena: Goodbye, Ava. Who knows, I might stop by sometimes. After all, youâre very stylish!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-75",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[25/27] Efena: Goodbye, Ava. Who knows, I might stop by sometimes. Maybe you'll have figured out that armour of yours.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-76",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Sybil: You should leave now or I'll be the one hitting you.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-18",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/2] Sybil: Calm down, Maxie.", "thefeathersflypart2-sybil-20", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/20] Efena: Honestly, I wouldn't blame him if he decided to skip this one out.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-77",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Efena: Oh, we get that very often. Especially with mechanics like you. Sorry.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-78",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/27] Efena: Hey, hey, calm down! I'm here to actually help you... in a way.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-79",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/27] Efena: I do believe we can all learn a thing or two about this.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-80",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/20] Efena: I don't think he'll skip this one. You look cute, Ava! That's your name, right? Handwriting's a little iffy.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-81",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[18/20] Efena: Right, right. AVA! Welcome to... the Council.", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-82", false);
        s.addSound("[2/3] Efena: Hey, Carl! We didn't ask!", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-83", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Efena: God, I hate to say it, but her mask was flawless.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-84",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/6] Efena: And WHY didn't you say so??", "thefeathersflypart2-efena-85", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Efena: Urgh. Look, there's only one thing I want to know.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-86",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Efena: soldier... Did you know, or did she trick you? Be very careful about what you're about to say.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-87",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/20] Efena: Somehow, you're able to control electromagic? I guess it's not exclusive to humans, then.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-88",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[25/27] Efena: Goodbye, Ava. Who knows, maybe I'll stop by sometimes. After all, you're very stylish!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-efena-89",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/9] Ava: Oh... So you showed up! I'm glad, I really am!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-1", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/9] Ava: It's time for me to show the Growth Accelerator to the Corkians.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/9] Ava: Look, this time I'll really try and reward you well, alright?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/9] Ava: Anyway! I have a plan. You see, I definitely can't easily get in the city.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/9] Ava: The Corkians have a council where they deal with their issues. We can try getting an audience.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/9] Ava: I know a way for me to get in the city. That's where you come in! There are some sentries to take care of.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/9] Ava: They're really old models though, somehow. I'll give you a jammer I made for this. Right-Click a robot to use it!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/9] Ava: Once you jam one robot, you'll have to jam all others within 20 seconds! So try to plan ahead and locate them all before jamming one!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[9/9] Ava: Tell me once you're ready. I'll throw you in there. I'll join you afterwards. You'll see!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-9",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/2] Ava: Well then, first off, take this!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-10", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Ava: Now, just stand still... I gotta try something on you...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-11",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Ava: Thanks! These robots were harmless but hey, better safe than sorry right?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-12",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Ava: Anyway, we need to get ready to meet the Corkian Council.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Ava: And I think... I need a disguise. I don't like hiding myself, but I don't have a choice.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-14",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Ava: Thanks to some plans I got, I know where to find some. Follow me!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-15",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Ava: Here we are! I'm pretty sure we can find some outfits in there.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] Ava: I'll stand here to quickly hide in case anyone comes.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-17",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] Ava: Just look around, and come back with what you think looks better!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-18",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] Ava: Yeah, I am letting you choose my outfit. Aren't you lucky? Go and get me the fanciest clothes!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-19",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/2] Ava: Shoot, I think someone's coming!! Come back!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-20", false);
        s.addSound("[2/2] Ava: ...Nevermind! Keep looking... Sorry...", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-21", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ava: I'm trusting you. We Avos aren't exactly into... Fashion. Then again, they're not into Electromagic either, so what do I know.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-22",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Alright, hold on...", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-23", false);
        s.addSound("[1/10] Ava: So, how do I look?!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-24", false);
        s.addSound("[2/10] Ava: I feel like... I'm about to go to work.", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-25", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/10] Ava: At the very least, I'll probably blend in very well!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-26",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/10] Ava: Now, I'm gonna be completely honest about this, so don't panic, but...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-27",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/10] Ava: I have... absolutely NO idea how we could even get an audience.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-28",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/10] Ava: I think we need to split up and try to find out how to get one from the Council.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-29",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/10] Ava: I'll be around the town center if ya need me for anything! I'll ask around. You should too!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-30",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/10] Ava: One last thing, though... Sorry if that's a little weird but...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-31",
                false);
        s.addSound("[9/10] Ava: ... What's your name?", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-32", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/10] Ava: soldier, huh? That's... A nice name. Well, good luck!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-33",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/10] Ava: I've already seen plenty of green in my lifetime, y'know.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-34",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/10] Ava: Well, I know you folks sure do love money. Maybe we can get noticed with this...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-35",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/10] Ava: Hmm... You know, this could actually work!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-36", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/10] Ava: I have no idea how this audience things works but I could try to get people to notice me!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-37",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/10] Ava: Well, we should split up and meet up later to see what information we have. Just ask around town!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-38",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/10] Ava: I'll be around the town center if you got any information!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-39",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/10] Ava: One last thing, though... Sorry if thats a little weird but...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-40",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/11] Ava: So, how do I look?!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-41", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/11] Ava: Ya got good taste! I always wanted to explore the ocean, y'know?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-42",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/11] Ava: Hey, thanks for helping me out so much. You've been such a huge help!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-43",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/11] Ava: Well, this isn't over, of course. And to tell you the truth...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-44",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/11] Ava: I, uh, have no idea how to get an audience... Sorry?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-45",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/11] Ava: I think we need to split up and try to find out how to get one.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-46",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/11] Ava: I'll be around the town center if ya need me for anything!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-47",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/11] Ava: One last thing, though... Sorry if that's a little weird but...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-48",
                false);
        s.addSound("[9/11] Ava: ... What's your name?", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-49", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[10/11] Ava: soldier, huh? That's... A nice name. Well, good luck!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-50",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[11/11] Ava: Oh, and check this mask out! Time to be Ava the human!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-51",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/10] Ava: I feel like... I'm not even supposed to be wearing this.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-52",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/10] Ava: This looks... Really, really cool though! ...Wait, where did you even find this?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-53",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/10] Ava: I saw this dog, and... Well, that's besides the point. You'll tell me later!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-54",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/10] Ava: Look, this audience thing is foreign to me but I feel like it won't really be an issue with this... thing.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-55",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/10] Ava: Well, we still need information on who to even talk to for that stuff... I'll ask around.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-56",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/10] Ava: You should too! I'll be around the town center! Come by once you got enough information!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-57",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/5] Ava: Oh, hey! I got something!!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-58", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Ava: Alright, so it's not really on the legal side of things, BUT apparently...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-59",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Ava: There's some sort of... Shady dealer you can buy an audience invitation from?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-60",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Ava: I'm sure there are other ways, but the dude should be in the castle to the east, first door to the left.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-61",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Ava: Do with that what you will. I guess I'll... Keep looking.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-62",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/9] Ava: Hey, what's up? I do have somethin'!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-63", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/9] Ava: Hmm... So we can go see a receptionist and they just might grant us an audience. Got it!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-64",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/9] Ava: So we go in, show her how cool we are, and I guess that'd work, huh?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-65",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/9] Ava: I'd say we have plenty of chances with that fancy armour you got me.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-66",
                false);
        s.addSound("[5/9] Ava: Oh, right, I had something too!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-67", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/9] Ava: There's apparently some sort of shady dude selling audience invitations!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-68",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/9] Ava: I believe it's in the castle to the east, on the first left? Though...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-69",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/9] Ava: I'm sure there are other ways to go about this. Like that receptionist, for one! So she's in the last room of the castle, right?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-70",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[9/9] Ava: In fact, if you want me to follow you there, I can do that! Just tell me!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-71",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Well, good luck searching!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-72", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Ava: So you found that weird dealer? Surely you're not thinking of...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-73",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Ava: I mean... Actually, that'd be a way to get an audience, for sure. What does he want?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-74",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Ava: [24 Emerald Blocks]? Is that a lot? I'm not human, y'know! Well, anyway!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-75",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Ava: Buy that if you want, but I'm certain there are other ways to obtain an audience. You don't really have to buy that.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-76",
                false);
        s.addSound("[5/5] Ava: Well, I'll just... Keep looking then.", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-77", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Ava: Oh? You found the dealer as well as one other way to get an audience?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-78",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Ava: 24 Emerald Blocks, huh? No clue if that's a lot. I'd say we should try your other way! What is it?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-79",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Ava: There's a receptionist for audiences? How convenient! We should go talk to her then!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-80",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Ava: It's... Apparently really hard? Oh... Well, that's not helpful. Maybe we can still give it a go?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-81",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Ava: It's difficult to get an audience? Well, it's worth a try, right? Maybe they'll see me as a wealthy lad!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-82",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Ava: It's... Apparently really hard? Huh. Well, we should still give it a go? I look fancy, surely they'll listen!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-83",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Ava: Buy from that weird dealer if ya want, but we should try to go see that receptionist. Tell me if you want me to follow you there.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-84",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Ava: Alright, let's go then. I'd say we should avoid the dealer, I definitely don't want to get on the bad side of the law!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-85",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/5] Ava: Hey. Ya got anythin'?", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-86", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Ava: Woah there, what's that letter? You actually got an invitation?!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-87",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/5] Ava: I... Wow. Well I'm impressed! I really am!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-88", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Ava: Did we even need a letter? That armour probably would've done the trick!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-89",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Ava: Well... If you want me to follow you, tell me. I've heard 'bout a receptionist in the far end of the castle, so maybe we should go there?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-90",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Well... You lead, I follow!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-91", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ava: I heard there was a dealer around here but... We have the letter, so let's just keep goin'.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-92",
                false);
        s.addSound("[3/3] Ava: ...Wow.", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-93", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Ava: Why thank you! I reckon you will search for an available time regarding an audience?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-94",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Ava: Uh... Greetings... We've heard that we should come here for-",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-95",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Ava: No, it's just that I, well... Nevermind, I do have a thing to show, it's uh...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-96",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Ava: The citizens said it was hard, huh? No kidding. Maybe we should've had something before strolling in.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-97",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Ava: Look, we'll figure out another approach. This can't end here! We need an audience invitation letter.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-98",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Ava: I'll head back to the town center, so if you want to talk I'll see ya there!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-99",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/8] Ava: Oh?! T-thank you... That's the first time someone told me such a thing!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-100",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/8] Ava: ...Will that grant me an audience with the Council?", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-101", false);
        s.addSound("[8/8] Ava: I- We'll... see what we can do.", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-102", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Ava: Look, I'm not good at being a human but even I know this is an absurd amount of money!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-103",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Ava: Do you think she'd actually take it? I'm not sure. We might have to find another way...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-104",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Ava: I'll go back to the town center. It's up to you if you want to risk all that money, if you even have it! We'll figure something else out.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-105",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Ava: Oh, uh, we, well I actually made a, uh, what's it called, uh...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-106",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Ava: That certainly didn't go well. But keep your head up! We got this!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-107",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Ava: There was a normal way to get an audience which is via a monthly competition of some sort, I think? We, uh... missed it. So that'll have to pass.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-108",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Ava: Now, for other... Unconventional ways... There was some panic by the Armour Merchant earlier today.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-109",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Ava: Check it out if you want, I won't cause trouble. I'd rather be the friendly neighbourhood mechanic!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-110",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Ava: There is apparently a dealer in the castle the receptionist's in, first entrance to the left. However, He charges emeralds...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-111",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Ava: I'm sure we can find a free alternative. I'm counting on ya! Just tell me if you want me to follow you!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-112",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Ava: That's crazy! 12 Liquified Emeralds? Is that how the world works?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-113",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Ava: It's just... I honestly don't care about listening to the law anymore.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-114",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Ava: Let's just get that audience. For one, there's some girl panicking by the Armour Merchant! Maybe she could help?",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-115",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Ava: As for another way, I don't know if you paid attention on our way to the receptionist, but...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-116",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Ava: There is apparently a dealer in there. He does charge money too, though. But surely not as much as that... wretched... lady! ...Sorry.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-117",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ava: Let's hope we get this right. You lead, I follow!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-118", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ava: Wait wait wait, I'm sure you're onto something but I'd rather not do anything fishy in town. Do what you wish, I'll hang around at the town center.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-119",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/8] Ava: Oh, uh, greetings! We have something for you!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-120", false);
        s.addSound("[8/8] Ava: WOO! Oh, sorry, we'll take our leave!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-121", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/8] Ava: Thank you so much! Sorry about my face, I'm... New in town. Bye!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-122",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Ava: I can't believe we're actually progressing! This is so exciting!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-123",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Ava: Alright, we need to test the machine before the audience. I've made some tweaks!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-124",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Ava: Meet me near the northern entrance if ya want a lift. Alternatively, you can just go by the Workshop if you're into walking!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-125",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Ava: Hey! I'm back in my original clothes. It feels much better...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-126",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Ava: Remember that hill next to the Workshop? We'll work there again. Tell me when you're ready for the lift.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-127",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ava: Here we go!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-128", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ava: There we are! Talk to me and I'll tell you all about the changes!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-129",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Ava: Do you remember how it worked last time? Don't worry, it's still fairly similar.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-130",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Ava: Once again, you'll have a remote. Simply click in the right orders. However!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-131",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Ava: Now, the machine requires a bit more... Dexterity.", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-132", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Ava: If you're really quick, the machine will charge up real fast!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-133",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Ava: If you're too slow however, it'd take a bit of time to charge up...",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-134",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Ava: Time is still limited too. Don't worry, this is practice for the Council! Tell me once you're ready!",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-135",
                false);
        s.addSound("[1/3] Ava: Alright, here's the remote!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-136", false);
        s.addSound("[2/3] Ava: A li'l push there...", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-137", false);
        s.addSound("[3/3] Ava: Alright, it's on you now!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-138", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ava: Oh no, time's up! It was supposed to be easy... Hold on, I'm booting it up again.",
                "thefeathersflypart2-ava-139",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ava: Oh, you're back! Talk to me so we can get started!", "thefeathersflypart2-ava-140", false);
