        // Underworld Crypt
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] General Graken: Aha, chap! Wonderful, the Ragni regiment's gotten its representative down 'ere. All rested up, I suppose, so let me give you an earful.",
                "underworldcrypt-generalgraken-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] General Graken: Those blighting zombies are all over the place. I tell ya, this skull's been giving the folk in Nemract the collywobbles. Just as I thought, they're all coming from here.",
                "underworldcrypt-generalgraken-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] General Graken: Now, I don't wish to alarm you old bean, but I believe we are in front of the literal gates to hell.",
                "underworldcrypt-generalgraken-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] General Graken: Not to worry chuck! Donât look so glum, I've called for aid from the nearby towns. Once they get here we'll give them a good kicking, and you've already gotten out of there before, ain't ya?",
                "underworldcrypt-generalgraken-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] General Graken: Now is finally our chance to take down his army... It will be a jolly difficult battle, knowing our opponent and what he's managed, even away from his lair.",
                "underworldcrypt-generalgraken-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] General Graken: Still, early days to say what he could be like in person! I'll take another route, but we'll meet in front of his door, right after crossing the river. Good luck, old bean!",
                "underworldcrypt-generalgraken-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] General Graken: Simply marvellous work, chap! You've made it this far, so no time to fill your boots. Be prepared, we are about to fight Charon's undead army.",
                "underworldcrypt-generalgraken-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] General Graken: We've lost a lot of good men on the way here, but I believe we can still throw a heavy punch.",
                "underworldcrypt-generalgraken-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/4] General Graken: You've earned a lot of respect from the boys this fight, better than all of us I'd say. For this fight, I'll let you direct the army.",
                "underworldcrypt-generalgraken-9",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/4] General Graken: Don't take it as a promotion though, old bean. It's only for this fight, although you'll be getting a medal of valor if I can wangle it! Charon's army is remarkably strong, we need as much help as we can get.",
                "underworldcrypt-generalgraken-10",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] General Graken: Aey- soldier careful now, the cretin must be lurking around here somewhere.",
                "underworldcrypt-generalgraken-11",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/3] Charon: I see you've brought aid, you aren't as foolish as I thought.",
                "underworldcrypt-charon-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/3] Charon: Tell me, how do you plan to defeat an army that cannot die!?",
                "underworldcrypt-charon-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Charon: Rise my minions! An undead army at my service, do you really think you stand a chance?",
                "underworldcrypt-charon-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Charon: You will suffer the same fate as those before you, summon thee souls from beneath!",
                "underworldcrypt-charon-4",
                false);

        // Corrupted Underworld Crypt
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] ???: How foolish. Just because you have overcome something once does not mean it will happen again.",
                "darkdescentdungeon-charon-4",
                true);
        s.addSound("[1/2] ???: BLARGH! My minions shall not let you pass!", "darkdescentdungeon-charon-5", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] ???: Aahrg, get the human! We can't let it pass by again!", "darkdescentdungeon-charon-6", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Corrupted Charon: Do you really think I will fall for that one again? An army likes yours is childsplay afor me! However, how do you plan to defeat an army that is already dead?",
                "darkdescentdungeon-charon-7",
                true);

        // Sand Swept tomb
        s.addSound("[1/1] ???: Who is the fool that has opened this accursed cage?", "sst-hashr-1", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] ???: You are not of the old empire... Not one of those who forced me in here.",
                "sst-hashr-2",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] ???: Why do you take arms against me? I only tried to save my people from my father!",
                "sst-hashr-3",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Hashr: If you insist on ending me, then I'll dispose of you like I did that wretched emperor!",
                "sst-hashr-4",
                true);

        // Corrupted Sand Swept tomb
        s.addSound("[1/1] ???: The fool returns... The cage shall claim you too.", "csst-hashr-1", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] ???: The glorious sands run red... I cannot understand it. I cannot understand you.",
                "csst-hashr-2",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] ???: Yet... New power runs forth at my fingertips. I may yet save this wretched land...",
                "csst-hashr-3",
                true);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Hashr: I will rule the red sands with this power under my control!", "csst-hashr-4", true);

        // Ice barrows
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Ghostly Voice: Soldier! I'm not sure it is wise to be here... An icy death awaits you if you proceed. A death that I will cause..",
                "icebarrows-ghostlyvoice-1",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Ghostly Voice: You must think you can save me? There is no cure for what I have.",
                "icebarrows-ghostlyvoice-2",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Ghostly Voice: I froze this land to allow it to heal.. People did not understand.. They came for me here, seeking revenge.",
                "icebarrows-ghostlyvoice-3",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Ghostly Voice: Even if you think you can cure me.. I can not allow you to try for if it were to fail my corrupted body would wreak havoc on the world!",
                "icebarrows-ghostlyvoice-4",
                true);

        // Corrupted Ice barrows
        s.addSound("[1/2] Ghostly Voice: I told you it would fail.", "cib-ghostlyvoice-1", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Ghostly Voice: Your noble deeds have allowed the darkness to take over my mind.",
                "cib-ghostlyvoice-2",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Ghostly Voice: It all seems clear to me now.. The struggle for life... Itâs futile. There need only be peaceful darkness.",
                "cib-ghostlyvoice-3",
                true);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Ghostly Voice: I will not let you stop me!", "cib-ghostlyvoice-4", true);

        // Undergrowth ruins
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] ???: I can sense your life force... it is very powerful. I shall take pleasure in draining it from your body!",
                "undergrowthruins-slykaar-1",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Slykaar: Troms used to beckon to my every need and desire... Even sacrifice it's own children for my magical defense!",
                "undergrowthruins-slykaar-2",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Slykaar: Now the city will truly get to witness what power they have discarded.. They will see they made the wrong call.",
                "undergrowthruins-slykaar-3",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Slykaar: Nothing and no one will stop me from sieging the city. Not even you!",
                "undergrowthruins-slykaar-4",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Slykaar: You have made the sacrifices of many be in total vain!",
                "undergrowthruins-slykaar-5",
                true);

        // Corrupted Undergrowth ruins
        s.addSound("[1/1] ???: More life...familiar life... Itâs you again. Isnât it?", "cur-slykaar-1", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Slykaar: Even in death... Wasnât I right? Wasnât I ALWAYS right? The corruption is here...",
                "cur-slykaar-2",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Slykaar: No saviours, no heroes. You being alive is nothing short of a miracle.",
                "cur-slykaar-3",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Slykaar: Your life will sustain my sanity. You will be...just another meal for me.",
                "cur-slykaar-4",
                true);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Slykaar: AAAGH! Idiot! Fool! Damnable THING! Exposed! Exposed! DIE!!", "cur-slykaar-5", true);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Slykaar: I donât want to die! I WONâT die! Go away! CEASE TO EXIST!", "cur-slykaar-6", true);
        s.addSound("[1/1] Slykaar: I... You... No...", "cur-slykaar-7", true);

        // Fallen factory
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] ????: ARE YOU INCAPABLE OF READING THE SIGN ON THE DOOR? THE FACTORY IS CLOSED. WE ARE NOT ACCEPTING VISITORS FOR TOURS RIGHT NOW.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-1",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] ????: FINE. IâM OPENING THE DOOR FOR YOU. TAKE A SHORT LOOK AROUND AND THEN LEAVE. THERE IS DANGEROUS EQUIPMENT HERE THAT ONLY OFFICIAL FACTORY ASSOCIATES SHOULD HANDLE.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-2",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] ????: OF COURSE, IF YOU ARE DEAD THEN THERE IS NO WAY FOR YOU TO TOUCH ANYTHING, AND MY ROBOTS ARE VERY GOOD CLEANERS, SO I THINK THIS NEW SOLUTION WILL WORK OUT FOR EVERYONE.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-3",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] ????: Unauthorized blockage in Factory Sector A2. Emergency maintenance will be performed in approximately 75 seconds. All regularly scheduled workers, please leave your posts until the blockage is cleared.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-4",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] ????: Blockage in Factory Sector A2 is now clear. All regularly scheduled workers, please return to your posts immediately.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-6",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] ????: WELL. DON'T YOU JUST FEEL SO PROUD OF YOURSELF. I DON'T KNOW WHAT YOU EXPECT TO ACCOMPLISH BY CRAWLING THROUGH THE VENTS. EXCEPT A FACE FULL OF HOT FUMES FROM THE FURNACE.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-7",
                true);
        s.addSound("[1/4] ????: Activating Main Production Line.", "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-8", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/4] ????: SINCE YOU SEEM TO BE INSISTENT ON STAYING, PERHAPS YOU WOULD BE INTERESTED IN TAKING A LOOK AT SOME OF THE MACHINERY CLOSE UP.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-9",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] ????: IF I WERE YOU, NOW WOULD BE A GOOD TIME TO RUN.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-10",
                true);
        s.addSound("[1/1] ????: I'VE HAD ENOUGH OF YOU.", "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-11", true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] ????: THAT WAS A LIE. I'M ACTUALLY STARTING TO ENJOY THIS.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-12",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] ????: YOU KNOW, THERE ISN'T A WAY FOR YOU TO GO FORWARD HERE. I COULD JUST KEEP THE DOOR LOCKED UNTIL YOU DROP FROM HUNGER.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-13",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] ????: WHOOPSIE-DOODLES. MY METAPHORICAL FINGER SLIPPED. AND BY THAT I MEAN I CLOSED THE DOOR MANUALLY.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-14",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] ????: Unexpected breach of locked door in Factory Sector 3A. Hastily-applied repairs due in approximately 30 seconds.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-15",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] ????: DO NOT TOUCH THAT BUTTON. YES, THE BIG SHINY ONE IN THE ROOM. IT WILL TURN ON THE POWER TO THE CLOCK TOWER MECHANISMS.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-16",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] ????: Activating Antikythera Clockwork Mechanism. All regularly scheduled workers, please evacuate the room immediately at risk of severe bodily harm and death.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-17",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Antikythera Supercomputer: YOU KNOW, YOU COULD SPARE ME A LOT OF TROUBLE IF YOU JUST GAVE UP WHAT YOU'RE DOING FOREVER. IT WOULD MOST LIKELY SPARE A LOT OF PEOPLE A LOT OF TROUBLE, ACTUALLY.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-18",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Antikythera Supercomputer: I SEE MY PERSUASIVE SKILLS HAVE NOT MOVED YOU. I THINK I'LL TRY AGAIN IN A LANGUAGE YOU SEEM TO KNOW INTIMATELY.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-19",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] ????: Unauthorized blockage in Factory Sector E1. Emergency maintenance will be performed in approximately 75 seconds. All regularly scheduled workers, please leave your posts until the blockage is cleared.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-20",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Antikythera Supercomputer: WELL THEN. EVEN THOUGH YOU GOT THROUGH THERE, YOU'LL BE SURPRISED TO KNOW I STILL HAVE ONE LAST LINE OF DEFENSE. I DOUBT EVEN YOU CAN GET PAST IT.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-21",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Antikythera Supercomputer: IF YOU ARE REALLY SO DESPERATE TO GET AT ME, THE KEY TO THE DOOR IS IN THIS PUPPY. EVEN SEEING YOUR ACTIONS THROUGHOUT THE REST OF MY FACTORY, I HAVE FAITH YOU WON'T KILL IT.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-22",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/4] Antikythera Supercomputer: WELL. WELL WELL WELL. WELL WELL WELL WELLY WELL WELL. I AM HONESTLY SHOCKED. REALLY, I AM. I TRULY STILL HAD SOME FAITH IN HUMANS. BEFORE YOU SHOWED UP.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-23",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Antikythera Supercomputer: THAT TRICK WON'T WORK, YOU KNOW. THERE'S NO VITAL PART OR DUCT ABOVE THERE TO ENTER. WHAT DID YOU HOPE TO ACCOMPLISH?",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-24",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Antikythera Core A: Oh, heya doc. Lemme tell ya, weirdest thing! Some bozo just ran up and shoved a bunch of scrap metal in my vent-",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-25",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Antikythera Supercomputer: YOU'VE QUICKLY BECOME NO LONGER ENTERTAINING TO WATCH. YOU REALLY SHOULDN'T GO IN THERE.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-26",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Antikythera Core B: Unauthorized personnel detected in Antikythera Auxiliary Core Duct B. Leave immediately, or be faced with lethal force and negative marks on your career record.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-27",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Antikythera Supercomputer: Primary ventilation duct A unblocked. Closing emergency maintenance hatch.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-28",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Antikythera Supercomputer: THAT IS EXTREMELY ANNOYING, CONSTANTLY CLEANING UP AFTER YOU. THERE ARE FAR MORE EFFICIENT WAYS OF DISPOSING OF SCRAP METAL AND UNNEEDED WASTE.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-29",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Antikythera Supercomputer: YOUR DESTRUCTIVE TENDENCIES KNOW NO BOUNDS. FIRST A DOOR. THEN A GRATE. THEN MY MONITOR. I'M SURPRISED YOU DIDN'T JUST THROW A MATCH AT THE FACTORY DOOR.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-30",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Antikythera Supercomputer: Antikythera Firewall Pass A accepted. Access granted. Please present Antikythera Firewall Pass B at the next checkpoint.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-31",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Antikythera Supercomputer: Antikythera Firewall Pass B accepted. Access granted. Welcome, Cerid. You may now enter the Antikythera Main Core Chamber.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-32",
                true);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Antikythera Main Core: SO YOU FOUND ME. CONGRATULATIONS. NOW PLEASE KINDLY LAY DOWN IN A CIRCUIT AND PRETEND TO BE A CONDUCTOR UNTIL YOUR BODY'S VITAL PROCESSES PERMANENTLY SHUT DOWN.",
                "fallenfactory-antikytherasupercomputer-33",
                true);

        // Legendary Island
        s.addSound(
                "[1/7] Legendary Attendant: Mo'in! Are you here to claim your rewards from the Legendary Challenge? Allow me to explain how the reward system works here.",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant1-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/7] Legendary Attendant: As you probably already know, there are four tiers of tokens. Similarly, there are four merchants to match those.",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant1-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/7] Legendary Attendant: You can purchase a base accessory at the Bronze Merchant.",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant1-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/7] Legendary Attendant: Then, at the Silver Merchant, you can upgrade your Bronze accessory into one of six types of Silver accessories.",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant1-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/7] Legendary Attendant: The six types are based on the five elements, along with another type that combines all five.",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant1-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/7] Legendary Attendant: The Gold Merchant allows you to upgrade a Silver accessory into a Gold accessory of the same element.",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant1-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/7] Legendary Attendant: The Diamond Merchant functions similarly. Thank you for participating in the Legendary Challenge!",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant1-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/9] Legendary Attendant: Mo'in, and welcome to Legendary Island, home of the Legendary Challenge!",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant2-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/9] Legendary Attendant: The Legendary Challenge consists of 10 powerful enemies, mostly based on some familiar faces.",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant2-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/9] Legendary Attendant: The Challenge is divided into four tiers: Bronze, Silver, Gold, and Diamond.",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant2-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/9] Legendary Attendant: The first 3 tiers have three challengers each, while the last, Diamond, has the final challenger.",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant2-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/9] Legendary Attendant: Between each fight, you'll have the option to forfeit to claim a reward, or continue to risk a greater reward.",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant2-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/9] Legendary Attendant: Someone will let you know what rewards you'll receive before you forfeit.",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant2-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/9] Legendary Attendant: If you fail during a fight, you'll receive no reward at all and will have to try again from the beginning.",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant2-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/9] Legendary Attendant: Between fights you'll be able to restock on resources if necessary.",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant2-8",
                false);
        s.addSound("[9/9] Legendary Attendant: Good luck!", "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant2-9", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Dr. Legendary: Mo'in, traveler, and welcome to... LEGENDARY ISLAND! The ultimate test of strength!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Dr. Legendary: With funding from the future province of Corkus, I went on a journey to study the strongest fighters in the world!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-2",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Dr. Legendary: This means that here, at Legendary Island, you can fight my creations, recreations of the most powerful beings of all time!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-3",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Dr. Legendary: There are 10 challengers for you to fight, and many prizes to collect!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-4",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Dr. Legendary: The first challenger you'll face is based off of a Mummy that I discovered hidden in the desert: The Mummyboard!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-5",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Dr. Legendary: You can challenge it now if you want, you can buy an entry ticket to the right.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-6",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] The Mummyboard: OS Version M-37 is now online. Systems estimate a 96.286573628% chance of success.",
                "legendaryisland-themummyboard-1", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Dr. Legendary: Impressive work against the Mummyboard, but that was only the first challenger! Things have only just begun!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-7",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Dr. Legendary: During my expedition across the world, funded by the amazing future province of Corkus, I happened upon a story about a doctor in Olux.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-8",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Dr. Legendary: Using samples of his so-called medicine, and stories about him, I managed to recreate the Plague Doctor as...",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-9",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/5] Dr. Legendary: the Virus Doctor!", "legendaryisland-drlegendary-10", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Dr. Legendary: You can continue and fight him now, or forfeit to your right, though you won't get much of a reward. The choice is yours.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-11",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Virus Doctor: Ah! It seems I have a subject for my next experiment. Don't worry, human, this will only hurt... a lot.",
                "legendaryisland-virusdoctor-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Dr. Legendary: Seems you were able to best the Virus Doctor, but this is still the Bronze tier, so don't get too cocky!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-12",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Dr. Legendary: After reading about a rare Gavel species with the properties of transformation, I knew I had to research it.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-13",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Dr. Legendary: Thanks to funding from Corkus, I managed to find it, the Corpus Accipientis, and created a golem with similar abilities.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-14",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Dr. Legendary: I call it the Corkus Accipientis! This will be the final battle of the Bronze tier!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-15",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Dr. Legendary: You can continue and challenge it now, or you can forfeit to your right for a small reward. It's up to you!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-16",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Corkus Accipientis: Scans indicate that your form is incredibly powerful. I will take it from you!",
                "legendaryisland-corkusaccipientis-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Dr. Legendary: Congratulations on defeating the Corkus Accipientis and completing the Bronze tier! If you win the next fight, you can start getting Silver tokens.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-17",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Dr. Legendary: My expedition, which was sponsored by Corkus, by the way, eventually lead me to the jungles of Wynn, where I heard rumors of an ancient idol.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-18",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Dr. Legendary: Though its name is rather hard to pronounce, I eventually managed to find and study the Matryoshka Idol.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-19",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Dr. Legendary: And now you can fight one of my most resilient creations, the Matrojan Idol!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-20",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Dr. Legendary: You can give it a shot now, or forfeit for a reward to your right, as usual.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-21",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Dr. Legendary: What a breathtaking fight! The Matrojan Idol, defeated! You're almost halfway there.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-22",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Dr. Legendary: During my travels, made possible by Corkus, I eventually stumbled into the Light Forest of Gavel, where I had a strange vision...",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-23",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Dr. Legendary: I saw... a villager, in his ultimate form, surrounded by mushrooms. The vision inspired me to create the next challenger.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-24",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Dr. Legendary: I call this robot... YahyaBot V4.04!", "legendaryisland-drlegendary-25", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Dr. Legendary: As always, you can forfeit to your right, or you can continue up ahead!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-26",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Dr. Legendary: Good grief, what is that thing?! And... YahyaBot! Wrecked! This is a disaster! Oh dear, what am I to do now...",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-27",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/2] Dr. Legendary: Oh- Traveler! It seems we've had a slight change in plans! Though this challenger is in pieces, if you can defeat this beast, I'll count it as a victory! Quickly, before it causes any more damage!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-28",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/6] Dr. Legendary: What a breathtaking fight! You've done it again! The Matrojan Idol, defeated! You're almost halfway there.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-29",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Dr. Legendary: Now. Ahem. As you will remember, this next challenger was intended as YahyaBot V4.04.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-30",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Dr. Legendary: But after your encounter with that beast last time, I got to thinking! What good is a fight without proper stakes? Wherein a single blow decides the match?!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-31",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Dr. Legendary: No, no, such a fight will not do for Legendary Island! As such, I have decided to scrap the previous inhabitant of middle Silver, and have replaced it with...",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-32",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Dr. Legendary: The Titanium R.A.T. R-4X! All fixed up and ready for a rematch!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-33",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Dr. Legendary: As always, if once was enough, you can forfeit to your right! Otherwise, continue up ahead!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-34",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Dr. Legendary: My word, that was certainly unexpected! A shame YahyaBot was destroyed, and yet... What a fight that was! Astounding.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-35",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Dr. Legendary: ...Ahem. Anyways, during my Corkus-sponsored expedition, I eventually found and scaled the legendary Tower of Ascension.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-36",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Dr. Legendary: Up there, I met a peculiar creature, dressed up as the spirit of Death itself! Despite being an impostor, its strength was still formidable.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-37",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Dr. Legendary: So the final fight of the Silver tier will be... Death Metal!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-38",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Dr. Legendary: As I'm legally obligated to remind you, you can forfeit to your right if you want.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-39",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Dr. Legendary: Ladies and gentlemen, performing you live from Legendary Stadium... it's Death Metal and the Ascendant Bosses!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-40",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Dr. Legendary: Just as before, an astounding victory against the Titanium R.A.T. R-4X! We'll, ah, have to sort out damages to the arena later.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-41",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Dr. Legendary: Anyways, during my Corkus-sponsored expedition, I eventually found and scaled the legendary Tower of Ascension.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-42",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Dr. Legendary: Drat! And those mechs were so expe- Oh! Great job defeating Death Metal!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-43",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Dr. Legendary: But this next one might be the end of you. The jungles of Wynn also spoke of a creature far more powerful and dangerous than the Idol.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-44",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Dr. Legendary: While I was unable to approach it myself, a man outside of a temple told me all about the monster in question.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-45",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Dr. Legendary: Which is why I am proud to present you the Mechorrupter of Worlds, the first enemy of the Gold Tier!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-46",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Dr. Legendary: The reward for forfeit, to your right, isn't too bad. You can stop now if you want, or risk it all and keep going!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-47",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Dr. Legendary: Congratulations! You've defeated your first challenger of the Gold tier! That's more than most can say.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-48",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Dr. Legendary: But you're bound to have heard of the next challenger. During my Corkus-funded travels, I heard every story of Bob known to man.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-49",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Dr. Legendary: I amassed all of my research into one of my finest creations! So I wish you good luck in defeating the one and only...",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-50",
                false);
        s.addSound("[4/5] Dr. Legendary: Robob's Reinvention!", "legendaryisland-drlegendary-51", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Dr. Legendary: While I applaud you for getting this far, there's never any shame in forfeitting off to the side. But the choice is still yours.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-52",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Robob: Only the most powerful warriors are worthy to face me. And by the looks of it, you barely made the cut.",
                "legendaryisland-robob-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/5] Dr. Legendary: Astounding! Very few have ever slain Robob. But this next challenger is known to very few, and still remains undefeated.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-53",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/5] Dr. Legendary: You've likely heard of Wybels. Have you heard stories of an orange one? They say an orange wybel is very intelligent and powerful.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-54",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/5] Dr. Legendary: I was unable to match its strength with electromagic alone, so I took a live Orange Wybel and... \"upgraded\" it into...",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-55",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/5] Dr. Legendary: The Orange Cybel, the final challenger of the Gold tier. If you defeat it, you'll even be able to challenge the Diamond tier.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-56",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/5] Dr. Legendary: If you truly believe in your strength, continue. If not, I'd advise you to forfeit now. Your reward is already sizable.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-57",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/1] Orange Cybel: You've wasted every chance you had to turn back. And you're really not going to like what happens now.",
                "legendaryisland-orangecybel-1",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/8] Dr. Legendary: Amazing! You even defeated the Cybel, my strongest creation. Well, except for one thing...",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-58",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/8] Dr. Legendary: With the help of Corkus, I travelled to the Hive, where I sought to model the final challenger after the legendary sorceress.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-59",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/8] Dr. Legendary: But... Qira declined. She said that if I tried anyway, she'd, erm... well, let's just say killing me was putting it too lightly.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-60",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/8] Dr. Legendary: It might be for the best, anyways. If the stories about her are true, her immense skill might be impossible to replicate.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-61",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/8] Dr. Legendary: So instead, I made something else, something entirely new...",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-62",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/8] Dr. Legendary: A mech suit that will be piloted by me, Doctor Legendary! With it, I might be one of the toughest foes you'll ever face!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-63",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[7/8] Dr. Legendary: But if you can defeat me, you'll get 1 Diamond Token, 7 Gold Tokens, 15 Silver Tokens, and 25 Bronze Tokens!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-64",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[8/8] Dr. Legendary: It's not too late to forfeit, if you want. But I have a feeling you've got one more fight in you.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-65",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/2] Dr. Legendary: So, you decided to come, then? Then let's see how you fare against the Champion of Legendary Island...",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-66",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/2] Dr. Legendary: Doctor Herbert von Legendary!", "legendaryisland-drlegendary-67", false);
        s.addSound(
                "[2/6] Dr. Legendary: I'm still in shock. I, the creator and controller of the strongest mechs in the world, have been defeated!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-68",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[3/6] Dr. Legendary: All of my research, sponsored by Corkus, of course, was still not enough. You have truly bested me.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-69",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[4/6] Dr. Legendary: I trust that you have received all of your tokens. You can make yourself a powerful accessory with all of those.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-70",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[5/6] Dr. Legendary: You've earned those tokens, but they might not be enough to maximize the power of an accessory.",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-71",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[6/6] Dr. Legendary: You'll have to go through the challenge all over again if you want more tokens. And I'm ready for a rematch any time!",
                "legendaryisland-drlegendary-72",
                false);
        s.addSound(
                "[1/3] Legendary Attendant: Hello, are you here to forfeit? If you quit now you will receive...",
                "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant3-1",
                false);
        s.addSound("[2/3] Legendary Attendant: 1 Bronze Token.", "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant3-2", false);
        s.addSound("[2/3] Legendary Attendant: 3 Bronze Tokens.", "legendaryisland-legendaryattendant3-3", false);
